3E%3Cp%3EAt%20least%20you%20can%20choose%20something%20more%20lively%20when%20protecting%20the%20phone%20with%20one%20of%20our%20picks%20of%20the%20best%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fbest-samsung-galaxy-z-fold-4-cases%5C%22%3EGalaxy%20Z%20Fold%204%20cases%3C%2Fa%3E%20or%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fbest-samsung-galaxy-z-fold-5-cases%5C%22%3EGalaxy%20Z%20Fold%205%20cases%3C%2Fa%3E.%20At%20the%20very%20least%2C%20make%20sure%20you%20add%20one%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fbest-samsung-galaxy-z-fold-5-screen-protectors%5C%22%3Ebest%20Z%20Fold%205%20screen%20protectors%3C%2Fa%3E%20-%20which%20will%20also%20fit%20the%20Fold%204.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3ESamsung%20Galaxy%20Z%20Fold%205%20vs.%20Fold%204%3A%20Displays%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222819%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Samsung%20Galaxy%20Z%20Fold%205%20internal%20display%20showing%20a%20green%20chameleon%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F659d6965ec62ab5daf81e2e7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221409%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Fold%205%20has%20a%20super%20crisp%20and%20sharp%20display.%3Cp%3EBrendan%20Griffiths%20%2F%20Business%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20specs%20comparison%20above%20shows%20that%20the%20front%20and%20internal%20AMOLED%20displays%20are%20the%20same%20on%20the%20Fold%205%20and%20Fold%204.%20Regarding%20image%20quality%20and%20refresh%20rate%20(still%20a%20silky%20120Hz)%2C%20we%20can't%20really%20complain%2C%20as%20both%20are%20excellent.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Fold%205%20does%20pull%20ahead%20in%20one%20aspect%2C%20though%2C%20as%20it's%20a%20bit%20brighter%20than%20the%20Fold%204%2C%20coming%20in%20at%201750%20nits%2C%20a%20nice%20bump%20up%20from%20the%201200%20nits%20of%20the%20Fold%204.%20Those%20numbers%20can%20be%20a%20little%20misleading%2C%20though%2C%20as%20the%20jump%20up%20isn't%20as%20big%20as%20those%20numbers%20suggest%20when%20you%20put%20the%20two%20phones%20side-by-side.%20It's%20noticeable%2C%20sure%2C%20but%20not%20by%20much.%20Direct%20sunlight%20or%20aggressive%20fluorescent%20tube%20lighting%20can%20still%20make%20things%20difficult%2C%20especially%20with%20light%20sometimes%20reflecting%20more%20off%20the%20display%20crease%20in%20such%20conditions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20looking%20at%20white%20images%2C%20like%20most%20website%20backgrounds%2C%20I%20noticed%20a%20slight%20yellow%20tinge%20to%20the%20Fold%205%2C%20and%20some%20colors%20appear%20a%20touch%20muted%20on%20the%20newer%20phone%2C%20too.%20Not%20in%20a%20bad%20way%2C%20though%2C%20as%20the%20contrast%20between%20shades%20is%20a%20touch%20more%20refined.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELet's%20talk%20about%20the%20crease.%20Despite%20a%20redesigned%20and%20flatter%20hinge%2C%20the%20crease%20has%20no%20visible%20reduction.%20It's%20not%20particularly%20visible%20when%20viewed%20head-on%20most%20of%20the%20time%2C%20though%2C%20and%20it%20really%20doesn't%20bother%20me%20that%20much.%20What%20bothers%20me%20is%20how%20Samsung%20isn't%20%3Cem%3Etrying%3C%2Fem%3E%20to%20flatten%20it%20out%20over%20the%20last%20three%20phones%20now%20when%20various%20Chinese%20foldables%20are%20getting%20very%20close%20to%20eradicating%20the%20crease%2C%20even%20if%20it%20seems%20to%20be%20coming%20at%20the%20cost%20of%20water%20resistance.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWithout%20fail%2C%20the%20crease%20is%20the%20first%20thing%20mentioned%20whenever%20anyone%20peeking%20over%20my%20shoulder%20asks%20me%20about%20the%20phone%2C%20and%20I%20feel%20there%20are%20a%20lot%20of%20potential%20buyers%20out%20there%20just%20waiting%20for%20the%20crease%20to%20go%20before%20making%20the%20jump.%20And%20for%20Apple%20to%20finally%20hop%20over%20the%20fence%20and%20join%20the%20foldable%20fun.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223085%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Samsung%20Galaxy%20Z%20Fold%205%20and%20Fold%204%20side%20by%20side%20showing%20internal%20displays%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F659d6982dcdb354a9855dfc7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221542%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Fold%205%20(left)%20has%20a%20brighter%20display%20than%20the%20Fold%204%20(right).%3Cp%3EBrendan%20Griffiths%20%2F%20Business%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhenever%20you're%20considering%20buying%20a%20foldable%20phone%2C%20you%20naturally%20might%20be%20more%20interested%20in%20what%20that%20big%20internal%20screen%20has%20to%20offer%2C%20and%20yeah%2C%20that%20is%20where%20all%20the%20magic%20happens.%20However%2C%20we%20must%20talk%20about%20the%20cover%20screen%20first%2C%20as%20you'll%20still%20use%20that%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20cover%20display%20is%20the%20same%20on%20the%20Fold%204%20and%20Fold%205%2C%20and%20that's%20a%20big%20problem.%20Or%2C%20more%20to%20the%20point%2C%20an%20irritatingly%20narrow%20one%20that's%20simply%20not%20working%20and%20the%20biggest%20reason%20not%20to%20buy%20%3Cem%3Eeither%3C%2Fem%3E%20phone.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20narrow%20ratio%20just%20isn't%20a%20good%20fit%20for%20most%20apps%20and%20websites%20as%20everything's%20a%20little%20off%2C%20with%20images%20often%20cropped%20weirdly%20both%20vertically%20and%20horizontally%20-%20dating%20apps%2C%20in%20particular%2C%20are%20basically%20unusable%20unless%20you%20open%20the%20phone.%20Scrolling%20through%20longer%20articles%20is%20a%20chore%2C%20with%20far%20fewer%20words%20fitting%20into%20each%20line.%20There's%20a%20reason%20nobody%20is%20buying%20Sony's%20similarly-ratioed%20Xperia%20phones.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20far%2C%20the%20biggest%20inconvenience%2C%20though%2C%20is%20the%20keyboard.%20I'll%20admit%2C%20I'm%20not%20the%20best%20mobile%20typist%3B%20I%20still%20mourn%20the%20Blackberry%20and%20its%20immaculate%20physical%20keyboard%2C%20but%20typing%20on%20the%20cover%20screen%20is%20as%20awful%20on%20the%20Fold%205%20as%20it%20was%20on%20the%20Fold%204.%20Both%20are%20better%20than%20the%20%3Cem%3Eslightly%3C%2Fem%3E%20narrower%20Fold%203.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEvery%20Google%20search%20or%20text%20reply%20is%20just%20about%20the%20wrong%20side%20of%20irritating%2C%20and%20these%20annoyances%20really%20add%20up%20on%20both%20phones.%20And%20just%20to%20be%20sure%2C%20I've%20extensively%20tried%20switching%20from%20the%20default%20keyboard%20to%20Google%2FMicrosoft%20options%2C%20but%20all%20with%20the%20same%20results.%20If%20you%20use%20swipe%20typing%20more%20often%20than%20not%2C%20you%20might%20fare%20a%20little%20better%2C%20but%20when%20needing%20to%20enter%20rarer%20words%20or%20names%2C%20you'll%20have%20to%20enter%20it%20manually%20with%20slow%2C%20precise%20taps%20that%20will%20give%20passers-by%20the%20impression%20you've%20just%20bought%20your%20first%20phone.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20telling%20how%20poor%20the%20typing%20experience%20is%20by%20the%20wave%20of%20relief%20I%20feel%20when%20I%20go%20back%20to%20my%20Note%2020%20Ultra.%20So%20much%20so%20it's%20clear%20I'm%20not%20ready%20to%20adopt%20Samsung's%20foldable%20tablet-phone%20hybrid%20full-time%20until%20the%20front%20display%20is%20widened.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOf%20course%2C%20typing%20on%20the%20internal%20display%20is%20fine%2C%20a%20two-handed%20affair%2C%20but%20opening%20up%20when%20you're%20on%20the%20move%20is%20not%20convenient.%20You%20won't%20want%20to%20leave%20it%20open%20all%20the%20time%20at%20home%20as%20to%20protect%20the%20screen.%20Accidentally%20applying%20weight%20to%20the%20rear%20of%20the%20device%20and%20going%20against%20the%20hinge%20could%20be%20a%20disaster.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe're%20hoping%20that%20the%20new%20wave%20of%20competition%20might%20wake%20Samsung%20up.%20Just%20before%20the%20Fold%205%20was%20released%20in%20the%20summer%20of%202023%2C%20Google%20released%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fgoogle-pixel-fold-review%5C%22%3EPixel%20Fold%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20a%20wider%20cover%20display%20that%20reviewers%20adored%20-%20not%20so%20much%20the%20gross%20early-adopter%20bezels%20on%20the%20inside%20display.%20Late%20in%202023%2C%20the%20OnePlus%20Open%20impressed%20with%20its%20wide%20front%20display%20and%20a%20great%20interior%20one%2C%20too%2C%20with%20thin%20bezels%20and%20a%20much%20more%20subtle%20crease.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ESamsung%20Galaxy%20Z%20Fold%205%20vs.%20Fold%204%3A%20Cameras%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Samsung%20Galaxy%20Z%20Fold%204%20and%20Fold%205%20side%20by%20side%20and%20closed%20showing%20hinge%20gap%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F659d6926dcdb354a9855df5f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222252%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EZ%20Fold%205%20(left)%20has%20a%20narrower%20hinge%20gap%20than%20the%20Fold%204%20(right).%3Cp%3EBrendan%20Griffiths%20%2F%20Business%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20cameras'%20specs%20and%20lenses%20have%20stayed%20the%20same%20between%20the%20Fold%204%20and%205.%20But%20the%20Fold%205%20does%20take%20ever%20so%20slightly%20better%20pictures%20thanks%20to%20improvements%20in%20the%20software%20and%20the%20added%20power%20coming%20from%20that%20Snapdragon%208%C2%A0Gen%202%20processor.%20Is%20it%20a%20night%20and%20day%20difference%3F%20Not%20at%20all%2C%20further%20adding%20weight%20to%20the%20argument%20that%20you%20shouldn't%20replace%20your%20phone%20yearly.%20Something%20I%20dearly%20wish%20Samsung%20and%20Apple%20would%20do%20themselves%2C%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20took%20a%20trip%20around%20Bath%20in%20the%20UK%20with%20the%20two%20cameras%2C%20taking%20photos%20of%20the%20same%20subjects%20at%20various%20ranges%20-%20without%20a%20tripod%2C%20sadly%2C%20so%20please%20forgive%20the%20modest%20differences%20in%20framing%20in%20the%20comparison%20shots%20below.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20struggled%20to%20tell%20the%20difference%20between%20the%20two%20with%20most%20shots.%20While%20admittedly%20a%20step%20or%20two%20behind%20the%20flagship%20like%20the%20S23%20Ultra%20or%20iPhone%2015%20Pro%20Max%2C%20both%20of%20Samsung's%20foldables%20take%20nice%2C%20detailed%20pictures%20on%20their%20default%20settings%20and%20are%20more%20than%20adequate%20for%20most%20uses.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20no%20surprise%20that%20the%20two%20phones%20take%20such%20similar%20pictures%2C%20given%20that%20the%20hardware%20hasn't%20changed%2C%20but%20when%20staring%20at%20similar%20shots%20side%20by%20side%20for%20way%20longer%20than%20I'd%20like%20to%20admit%2C%20the%20main%20differences%20seem%20to%20be%20in%20shadows%20and%20color%20detail.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Z%20Fold%204%20adds%20in%20extra%20light%20to%20darker%20areas%20and%20shadows%2C%20whereas%20the%20Fold%205%20does%20a%20better%20job%20of%20respecting%20the%20actual%20shadows%20to%20provide%20a%20more%20accurate%20image.%20As%20for%20color%2C%20look%20at%20the%20sandstone%20bricks%20or%20the%20tree%20trunks%20in%20the%20photos%20below%2C%20and%20you'll%20notice%20they%20have%20a%20bit%20more%20life%20on%20the%20Fold%205%20than%20the%20Fold%204%2C%20making%20them%20a%20bit%20more%20appealing.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20zooming%20in%20%3Cem%3Eafter%3C%2Fem%3E%20taking%20a%20picture%2C%20the%20Fold%205%20doesn't%20break%20up%20as%20quickly.%20But%20using%20the%2030x%20zoom%20on%20distant%20objects%20still%20produces%20a%20blurred%20watercolor%20effect%3B%20even%2020x%20is%20a%20bit%20muddy%20on%20busier%20scenes.%2010x%2C%20though%2C%20is%20seemingly%20the%20sweet%20spot%20for%20most%20ranged%20shooting%20on%20both%20phones.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22raw%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Ciframe%20width%3D%5C%22100%25%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.knightlab.com%2Flibs%2Fjuxtapose%2Flatest%2Fembed%2Findex.html%3Fuid%3D74ac5950-af09-11ee-9ddd-3f41531135b6%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22400%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22raw%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Ciframe%20width%3D%5C%22100%25%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.knightlab.com%2Flibs%2Fjuxtapose%2Flatest%2Fembed%2Findex.html%3Fuid%3D8aefc12e-af0a-11ee-9ddd-3f41531135b6%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22400%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22raw%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Ciframe%20width%3D%5C%22100%25%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.knightlab.com%2Flibs%2Fjuxtapose%2Flatest%2Fembed%2Findex.html%3Fuid%3De7ef8e42-af08-11ee-9ddd-3f41531135b6%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22400%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22raw%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Ciframe%20width%3D%5C%22100%25%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.knightlab.com%2Flibs%2Fjuxtapose%2Flatest%2Fembed%2Findex.html%3Fuid%3Dedcf3d4c-af0a-11ee-9ddd-3f41531135b6%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22400%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22raw%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Ciframe%20width%3D%5C%22100%25%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.knightlab.com%2Flibs%2Fjuxtapose%2Flatest%2Fembed%2Findex.html%3Fuid%3Dd3052ddc-af0a-11ee-9ddd-3f41531135b6%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22400%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22raw%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Ciframe%20width%3D%5C%22100%25%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.knightlab.com%2Flibs%2Fjuxtapose%2Flatest%2Fembed%2Findex.html%3Fuid%3D8149167a-af14-11ee-9ddd-3f41531135b6%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22400%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22raw%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Ciframe%20width%3D%5C%22100%25%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.knightlab.com%2Flibs%2Fjuxtapose%2Flatest%2Fembed%2Findex.html%3Fuid%3Dbb0aa0ae-af14-11ee-9ddd-3f41531135b6%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22400%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20hope%20the%20Fold%206%20can%20improve%20with%20some%20of%20the%20AI%20tech%20coming%20to%20the%20S24%2C%20as%20we%20should%20be%20getting%20flagship%20experiences%20here%20and%20not%20feeling%20FOMO.%20Sure%2C%20most%20buyers%20might%20barely%20notice%20the%20difference%2C%20but%20at%20%241800%2C%20that's%20not%20the%20point.%20Foldables%20aren't%20new%20anymore%2C%20and%20that%20price%20should%20get%20you%20the%20very%20best%20a%20brand%20has%20to%20offer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3ESamsung%20Galaxy%20Z%20Fold%205%20vs.%20Fold%204%3A%20Battery%20life%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBoth%20phones%20pack%20a%204%2C400%20mAh%20battery%2C%20which%20still%20lags%20behind%20the%205%2C000%20in%20Samsung's%20S23%20Ultra.%20That%20being%20said%2C%20I%20found%20I%20could%20comfortably%20get%20through%20a%20whole%20day%20of%20average%20use%20regularly%20with%20both%20phones%20with%20similar%20screen-on%20times%20of%208-10%20hours%20each.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECharging%20speeds%20on%20the%20Fold%205%20remain%20locked%20to%2025W%2C%20so%20you're%20looking%20at%20around%2085%20minutes%20from%20flat%20to%20full%20as%20charging%20speeds%20slow%20towards%20the%20end%20for%20battery%20preservation%2C%20or%2030%20minutes%20to%2050%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYes%2C%20given%20the%20Fold%205%20costs%20way%20beyond%20a%20flagship%20phone%20price%2C%20it%20really%20should%20have%2045W%20charging%20speeds%20as%20an%20option%20by%20now%2C%20but%20in%20reality%2C%20you're%20not%20saving%20a%20huge%20amount%20of%20time%20between%20the%20two%20(that%2085-minute%20charge%20would%20be%20closer%20to%20sixty%20minutes).%20I'd%20always%20opt%20for%20a%20larger%20battery%20over%20faster%20charging.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20have%20found%20that%20the%20battery%20on%20the%20newer%20Fold%205%20gets%20hotter%20than%20the%20Fold%204's.%20Charging%20the%20phone%20or%20downloading%20large%20files%2Fupdates%20makes%20the%20device%20heat%20up%20quickly.%20Oddly%2C%20it%20doesn't%20do%20the%20same%20when%20gaming%20to%20the%20same%20extent.%20If%20anything%2C%20I%20was%20surprised%20at%20how%20%3Cem%3Elittle%3C%2Fem%3E%20it%20heats%20up%20over%20an%20hour%20or%20so%20playing%20Call%20of%20Duty%20or%20Diablo%20Immortal%20on%20high%20settings%2C%20as%20previous%20models%20start%20to%20get%20hot%20after%20about%2015%20minutes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Samsung%20Galaxy%20Z%20Fold%204%20and%20Fold%205%20side%20by%20side%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F659fce81dcdb354a98569db2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222252%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Fold%20devices%20are%20excellent%20for%20productivity%20and%20watching%20media%20content.%3Cp%3EBrendan%20Griffiths%20%2F%20Business%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%3ESamsung%20Galaxy%20Z%20Fold%205%20vs.%20Fold%204%3A%20Price%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Samsung%20Galaxy%20Z%20Fold%205%20launched%20at%20%241799%2F%C2%A31749%20for%20the%20256GB%20model%2C%20matching%20the%20launch%20price%20of%20the%20Fold%204%20in%20the%20US%20-%20a%20weaker%20pound%20and%20inflation%20saw%20the%20new%20model's%20price%20rise%20%C2%A3100%20in%20the%20UK%2C%20though.%20So%20yes%2C%20we're%20still%20a%20long%20way%20off%20being%20able%20to%20feature%20tablet-esque%20foldables%20in%20our%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fbest-budget-android-phone%5C%22%3Ebest%20budget%20Android%20phone%3C%2Fa%3E%20guide.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20with%20other%20recent%20Samsung%20launches%2C%20Samsung%20offered%20a%20free%20storage%20upgrade%20(the%20512GB%20model%20was%20going%20for%20the%20256GB%20price)%2C%20but%20that%20offer%20has%20expired.%20Samsung%20and%20the%20big%20carriers%20regularly%20run%20various%20trade-in%20deals%2C%20although%20the%20prices%20vary%20dramatically%20and%20may%20fluctuate%20at%20different%20times%20of%20year.%20A%20few%20months%20after%20launch%2C%20we%20saw%20up%20to%20%24250%20off%20an%20unlocked%20Fold%205%20model%20at%20Amazon%2C%20so%20going%20unlocked%20is%20worth%20considering.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20for%20the%20Fold%204%2C%20it's%20no%20longer%20sold%20at%20Samsung's%20site.%20Prices%20at%20retail%20vary%20widely%2C%20but%20we%20expect%20most%20stock%20to%20sell%20out%20soon%2C%20or%20you'll%20be%20looking%20at%20used%2Frefurbished%20options%2C%20which%20are%20certainly%20worth%20a%20look%20if%20you%20can%20take%20at%20least%20%24500%20off%20that%20MSRP.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EWhich%20one%20should%20you%20buy%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223756%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Samsung%20Galaxy%20Z%20Fold%204%20and%20Fold%205%20side%20by%20side%20showing%20front%20displays%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F659d6926dcdb354a9855df5e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222114%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EZ%20Fold%204%20on%20the%20left%20and%20Z%20Fold%205%20on%20the%20right.%20We%20think.%3Cp%3EBrendan%20Griffiths%20%2F%20Business%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Fold%205%20is%20the%20better%20foldable%20phone%2C%20but%20the%20Fold%204%20is%20certainly%20still%20worth%20considering%20if%20you%20can%20get%20an%20appropriate%20discount.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhat%20about%20upgrading%20from%20the%204%20to%20the%205%3F%20There%20needed%20to%20be%20more%20'newness'%20or%20general%20improvements%20to%20the%20Fold%205%20to%20justify%20the%20extra%20spend.%20If%20you%20already%20have%20the%20Fold%204%2C%20I%20suggest%20you%20stick%20with%20it%20for%20another%20year.%20Given%20the%20Pixel%20Fold%20and%20OnePlus%20Open%20have%20entered%20the%20arena%2C%20I'd%20be%20shocked%20if%20Samsung%20rolls%20out%20another%20indifferent%20upgrade%20for%20the%20Fold%206.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20picked%20up%20a%20Fold%202%20or%203%20a%20few%20years%20ago%2C%20then%20yes%2C%20this%20is%20a%20decent%20upgrade%20as%20you'll%20appreciate%20the%20improvements%20more%2C%20and%20your%20window%20for%20getting%20any%20decent%20trade-in%20value%20on%20those%20models%20is%20rapidly%20closing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fsamsung-galaxy-z-fold-5-vs-galaxy-z-fold-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704974751000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F659fccea43bb77284b9c2681%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fsamsung-galaxy-z-fold-5-vs-galaxy-z-fold-4%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Our%20Samsung%20Galaxy%20Z%20Fold%205%20vs.%20Fold%204%20head-to-head%20compares%20specs%2C%20cameras%2C%20displays%2C%20and%20more%20after%20months%20of%20testing.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Brendan%20Griffiths)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fsamsung-galaxy-z-fold-5-vs-galaxy-z-fold-4%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Astrobotic's%20lander%20might%20still%20travel%20far%20enough%20to%20reach%20the%20moon%2C%20but%20the%20moon%20won't%20be%20there%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20picture%20taken%20from%20an%20onboard%20camera%20shows%20on%20of%20the%20sides%20of%20Astrobotic's%20Peregrine%20lander.%20A%20small%20sliver%20of%20light%20is%20seen%20on%20the%20right%20hand%20side.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F659e82cb6979d7371821e999%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20new%20snap%20of%20the%20Peregrine%20lander%20was%20shared%20by%20Astrobotic%20on%20X%20on%20Tuesday.%3Cp%3EAstrobotic%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EAstrobotic's%20spacecraft%20could%20make%20it%20as%20high%20as%20the%20moon%20but%20it%20won't%20meet%20it.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20lander%20is%20still%20going%2C%20despite%20a%20fuel%20leak%20that%20dashed%20hopes%20of%20a%