ek%20after%20being%20told%20to%20return%20to%20the%20office%20says%20he's%20not%20sure%20how%20long%20he%20can%20keep%20it%20up%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222121%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Unrecognizable%20Man%20With%20Bag%20And%20Suitcase%20Walking%20In%20Airport%2C%20Rear%20View%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F659fcaa143bb77284b9c2621%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221414%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EProstock-Studio%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EWall%20Street%20Journal%20reporter%20Chip%20Cutter%20is%20a%20supercommuter.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHe%20flies%20from%20Columbus%20to%20NYC%20once%20a%20week%20to%20spend%20three%20days%20in%20the%20office.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHe%20blew%20his%20budget%20and%20burned%20through%20air%20miles%2C%20but%20says%20it's%20worth%20it%20for%20the%20cheap%20rent%20and%20time%20with%20family%20in%20Ohio.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EA%20Wall%20Street%20Journal%20reporter%20says%20his%20weekly%20commute%20from%20Ohio%20to%20NYC%20drains%20him%20but%20that%20it's%20worth%20it%20because%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcost-of-living-midwest-cities-prices-housing-rent-medical-energy-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Echeaper%20rent%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20extra%20time%20with%20his%20family%20in%20the%20Buckeye%20State.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChip%20Cutter%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wsj.com%2Flifestyle%2Ftravel%2Fim-a-supercommuter-heres-what-its-really-like-f88702b0%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewrote%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20The%20Journal%20that%20he%20flies%20from%20Columbus%20to%20JFK%20Airport%20once%20a%20week%2C%20staying%20in%20hotels%20and%20leaving%20spare%20clothes%20in%20the%20office.%20He's%20been%20commuting%20like%20this%20for%20more%20than%20a%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20began%20as%20a%20postpandemic%20experiment%20of%20flying%20to%20and%20from%20New%20York%20each%20week%20has%20turned%20into%20what%20I%20am%20hesitant%20to%20call%20a%20lifestyle%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECutter%20moved%20back%20to%20Ohio%2C%20his%20home%20state%2C%20during%20the%20pandemic.%20When%20The%20Journal%20asked%20him%20to%20return%20to%20its%20Manhattan%20office%20three%20days%20a%20week%2C%20he%20was%20%26quot%3Bunderwhelmed%26quot%3B%20by%20the%20properties%20he%20could%20afford%20in%20NYC%2C%20he%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20he%20latched%20onto%20the%20idea%20of%20becoming%20a%20so-called%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsuper-commuters-hybrid-work-wfh-business-travel-office-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esupercommuter%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUsing%20back-of-the-envelope%20math%2C%20I%20thought%20I%20could%20keep%20my%20expenses%E2%80%94rent%20in%20Ohio%2C%20plus%20travel%20costs%E2%80%94at%20or%20below%20the%20price%20of%20a%20nice%20New%20York%20studio%2C%20or%20roughly%20%243%2C200%20a%20month%2C%26quot%3B%20Cutter%20wrote.%20%26quot%3BThe%20challenge%20felt%20oddly%20thrilling.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Mondays%20Cutter%20wakes%20up%20at%204%3A15%20a.m.%20to%20catch%20a%206%20a.m.%20flight%2C%20and%20if%20there%20are%20no%20disruptions%20he%20can%20make%20it%20door-to-door%20in%20three%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20he%20first%20started%20commuting%20between%20states%2C%20Cutter%20burned%20through%20his%20hotel-loyalty%20points%20by%20staying%20in%20luxury%20hotels.%20He%20also%20%26quot%3Brepeatedly%26quot%3B%20had%20to%20rebook%20flights%20and%20stump%20up%20for%20an%20extra%20night%20in%20a%20hotel%20to%20meet%20work%20deadlines%2C%20he%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20instead%2C%20he%20started%20looking%20for%20cheaper%20accommodation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSometimes%20I%20sleep%20in%20a%20different%20New%20York%20City%20hotel%20room%20every%20night%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote%20in%20the%20Journal%20article.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20hotel%20prices%20are%20high%2C%20I%20property-surf%20to%20find%20a%20lower%20rate.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20wrote%20that%20hotel%20room%20prices%20fluctuate%20even%20on%20the%20check-in%20day%2C%20%26quot%3Bso%20instead%20of%20booking%20in%20advance%2C%20I'd%20wait%20to%20pull%20the%20trigger%20until%2010%20p.m.%20some%20days%20after%20the%20rates%20fell.%26quot%3B%20Sometimes%2C%20he%20stays%20at%20friends'%20apartments%2C%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20this%2C%20he%20still%20ran%20low%20on%20air%20miles%2C%20and%20blew%20his%20budget%20by%2015%25%2C%20he%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWorking%20in%20a%20city%20without%20a%20permanent%20home%20took%20a%20toll%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote.%20%26quot%3BI%20came%20to%20dread%20the%20go-to%20question%20asked%20at%20parties%20and%20work%20events%20in%20New%20York%3A%20'So%20where%20do%20you%20live%3F'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStaying%20in%20hotel%20rooms%20without%20kitchen%20facilities%20means%20that%20he%20has%20to%20rely%20on%20easy%20late-night%20dinners%20he%20can%20buy%20from%20a%2024-hour%20store%2C%20like%20yogurt%20and%20fruit%2C%20Cutter%20wrote.%20And%20so%20that%20he%20can%20pack%20light%2C%20he%20keeps%20shoes%20under%20his%20desk%20in%20the%20office%20and%20spare%20outfits%20on%20a%20coat%20rack.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20despite%20this%2C%20his%20commute%20means%20he%20can%20spend%20more%20time%20with%20family%20and%20avoid%20paying%20New%20York%20rent.%20%26quot%3BIt%20has%20been%20worth%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Cutter%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.foxbusiness.com%2Flifestyle%2Fnyc-supercommuter-avoids-high-nyc-rent-traveling-ohio-home-every-week%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFox%20Business%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20an%20interview.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20still%20enjoy%20having%20one%20foot%20in%20the%20Midwest%20and%20one%20on%20the%20East%20Coast%2C%20though%20I'm%20not%20sure%20how%20long%20I%20can%20keep%20it%20up%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote%20in%20the%20Journal%20article.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3