t-iphone%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EApple%20iPhones%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20they%20are%20exclusive%20to%20Apple%20mobile%20iOS%20devices.%20You%20can%20download%20and%20use%20App%20Store%20apps%20on%20iPhones%2C%20iPads%2C%20and%20iPod%20Touch.%20(The%20iPod%20Touch%20was%20discontinued%20as%20of%202022%2C%20but%20it%20is%20still%20supported%20at%20the%20time%20of%20this%20writing.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat's%20the%20Apple%20App%20Store%20called%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Apple%20App%20store%20is%20called%20the%20App%20Store.%20When%20first%20unveiled%20in%20the%20summer%20of%202008%2C%20the%20App%20Store%20was%20called%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmost-expensive-iphone-apps-2010-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EiPhone%20App%20Store%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Today%2C%20it's%20simply%20called%20the%20App%20Store%2C%20which%20is%2C%20of%20course%2C%20different%20than%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fevery-apple-store-in-the-united-states-photos-2019-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EApple%20Store%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20company's%20brick-and-mortar%20retail%20locations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20is%20the%20difference%20between%20the%20Apple%20Store%20and%20the%20App%20Store%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20App%20Store%20is%20the%20app%20on%20your%20phone%20or%20tablet%20to%20download%20apps%3B%20the%20Apple%20Store%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20is%20where%20you%20buy%20an%20iPhone%2C%20iPad%2C%20MacBook%2C%20and%20other%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fapple-iphone-mac-products-great-classic-boring-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EApple%20products%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Apple%20Store%20refers%20to%20hundreds%20of%20physical%20locations%20worldwide%20and%20on%20Apple's%20website.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20are%20the%20differences%20between%20Google%20Play%20and%20App%20Store%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20most%20appreciable%20ways%2C%20Google%20Play%20and%20the%20App%20Store%20are%20comparable.%20Google%20Play%20is%20the%20vehicle%20by%20which%20Android%20mobile%20device%20users%20download%20apps%2C%20whereas%20the%20App%20Store%20is%20the%20portal%20for%20iOS%20device%20users.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20main%20difference%20is%20volume%3A%20Google%20Play%20offers%20more%20apps%2C%20but%20the%20App%20Store%20has%20a%20longer%20and%20more%20stringent%20app%20review%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ECan%20I%20delete%20and%20reinstall%20the%20Apple%20Store%20app%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20cannot%20delete%20the%20App%20Store%20app%3B%20it%20is%20one%20of%20the%20few%20native%20and%20permanent%20iOS%20apps.%20You%20can%20hide%20the%20App%20Store%20app%20and%20other%20such%20permanent%20apps%20if%20you%20wish.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20do%20so%2C%20tap%20and%20hold%20on%20the%20App%20Store%20icon%2C%20then%20tap%20%26quot%3BRemove%20App%26quot%3B%20in%20red%20letters%20at%20the%20bottom%20of%20the%20popup%20window.%20Next%2C%20tap%20%26quot%3BRemove%20from%20Home%20Screen.%26quot%3B%20This%20will%20hide%20the%20App%20Store%20app%2C%20but%20it%20can%20be%20retrieved%20via%20search%20or%20the%20%26quot%3BSettings%26quot%3B%20app%20at%20any%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20happens%20if%20you%20delete%20Apple%20apps%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EA%20deleted%20app%20can%20always%20be%20redownloaded%20and%20reinstalled%2C%20and%20in%20cases%20where%20you%20had%20a%20subscription%20(paid%20or%20not)%2C%20you%20may%20well%20be%20able%20to%20pick%20up%20where%20you%20left%20off%20with%20no%20loss%20of%20data%20or%20functionality.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20in%20many%20cases%2C%20deleting%20an%20Apple%20app%20can%20delete%20all%20associated%20data%2C%20meaning%20you%20would%20be%20at%20square%20one%20if%20you%20reinstalled%20it.%20Deleting%20apps%20can%20also%20have%20other%20impacts%2C%20both%20positive%20and%20negative.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20deleting%20apps%20may%20free%20up%20space%20and%20let%20you%20store%20more%20photos%20or%20enjoy%20faster%20processing%20speed%2C%20but%20deleting%20an%20app%20from%20your%20phone%20means%20it's%20no%20longer%20usable%20anywhere.%20For%20example%2C%20removing%20a%20music%20app%20from%20your%20phone%20can%20also%20delete%20it%20from%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fbest-apple-watch%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EApple%20Watch%3C%2Fa%3E%20you%20always%20used%20for%20tunes%20at%20the%20gym.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fapple-app-store%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704971761000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F659bd939ec62ab5daf816b94%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fapple-app-store%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Apple's%20App%20Store%20contains%20millions%20of%20apps%20to%20download%20and%20install%20to%20your%20iOS%20device.%20Here's%20how%20it%20works.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22stevenjohn23%40gmail.com%20(Steven%20John)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A17%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fapple-app-store%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22SC%20Issues%20Contempt%20Notices%20to%20Gujarat%20Officials%20Over%20Police%20Custody%20of%20a%20Businessman%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F25222448%2FSupreme-Court-1.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20January%2011%2C%20came%20down%20heavily%20on%20the%20Gujarat%20government%E2%80%99s%20additional%20chief%20secretary%20(home)%2C%20police%20officials%2C%20and%20an%20additional%20chief%20magistrate%20over%20sending%20a%20businessman%20to%20police%20custody%20despite%20the%20apex%20court%20granting%20him%20anticipatory%20bail.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20a%20gross%20contempt%20of%20the%20court%E2%80%99s%20order%20on%20the%20face%20of%20the%20record.%20How%20could%20he%20have%20been%20taken%20into%20custody%3F%20How%20could%20the%20investigating%20officer%20(IO)%20dare%20to%20seek%20the%20remand%3F%E2%80%9D%20asked%20Justice%20Sandeep%20Mehta%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2Fsc-contempt-notice-to-io-magistrate-over-custody-of-gujarat-businessman-9104218%2F%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20the%20%3Cem%3EIndian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20issued%20contempt%20notices%20to%20the%20authorities%20concerned.%20%E2%80%9CLet%20this%20be%20corrected%20in%20some%20manner.%20The%20IO%20(investigating%20officer)%20and%20magistrate%20must%20learn%20some%20lessons%20from%20this.%20We%20will%20issue%20the%20notice%20for%20contempt%20to%20the%20magistrate%20also.%20Is%20this%20the%20manner%20in%20which%20they%20deal%20with%20the%20Supreme%20Court%E2%80%99s%20Order%3F%E2%80%9D%20asked%20Justice%20B.R.%20Gavai%2C%20another%20judge%20on%20the%20division%20Bench.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBusinessman%20Tusharbhai%20Rajnikantbhai%20Shah%2C%20a%20resident%20of%20Surat%2C%20has%20been%20accused%20in%20a%20cheating%20case.%20He%20was%20granted%20an%20interim%20anticipatory%20bail%20on%20December%208%2C%202023.%20According%20to%20Shah%2C%20he%20appeared%20before%20the%20police%20on%20December%2011%20to%20support%20the%20investigation%20but%20was%20arrested%20and%20released%20on%20bail%20the%20same%20day.%20The%20police%20then%20moved%20a%20remand%20application%20on%20December%2013%20before%20a%20local%20court%20resulting%20in%20his%20police%20custody%20for%20four%20days%2C%20Shah%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJustice%20Mehta%20was%20livid%2C%20noting%20that%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20very%20filing%20of%20the%20(remand)%20application%20was%20contempt%20on%20the%20face%20of%20it%E2%80%9D%20and%20called%20it%20%E2%80%9Cblatant%20illegal%20custody%20for%20four%20days!%E2%80%9D%20Justice%20Gavai%20then%20added%2C%20%E2%80%9CLet%20the%20Magistrate%20and%20the%20IO%20be%20inside%20for%20four%20days.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20this%20juncture%2C%20additional%20solicitor%20general%20S.V.%20Raju%2C%20who%20appeared%20on%20behalf%20of%20the%20Gujarat%20government%2C%20told%20the%20court%20that%20it%20was%20a%20%E2%80%9Cblunder%E2%80%9D%20on%20the%20part%20of%20the%20investigating%20officer%20and%20tendered%20an%20apology.%20When%20the%20court%20sought%20a%20CCTV%20recording%20from%20the%20police%20station%2C%20Raju%20responded%20that%20it%20was%20not%20functional.%20To%20this%2C%20Justice%20Gavai%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%20shows%20the%20conduct.%20On%20the%20very%20same%20day%2C%20it%20is%20not%20functioning!%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJustice%20Mehta%20chimed%20in%2C%20by%20saying%2C%20%E2%80%9CThis%20was%20expected.%20It%E2%80%99s%20intentional%E2%80%A6%E2%80%9D.%20He%20then%20went%20on%20to%20ask%2C%20%E2%80%9CIn%20a%20civil%20nature%20case%2C%20why%20remand%20is%20required%3F%20A%20murder%20weapon%20was%20to%20be%20recovered%20or%20what%3F%E2%80%9D.%20Justice%20Mehta%20specifically%20said%20the%20authorities%20must%20explain%20why%20CCTV%20was%20not%20functioning%20on%20the%20said%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20asked%20authorities%20concerned%20to%20file%20affidavits%20explaining%20their%20response%20while%20adding%20that%20it%20may%20even%20possibly%20ask%20the%20state%20police%20chief%20to%20take%20those%20charged%20with%20contempt%20of%20court%20into%20custody%20and%20to%20prison.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Surat%20police%20commissioner%20Ajay%20Kumar%20Tomar%20told%20%3Cem%3EIE%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20he%20was%20unaware%20of%20the%20incident%20and%20would%20get%20the%20matter%20checked%20from%20his%20office.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShah%E2%80%99s%20advocate%20Syed%20accused%20Surat%20Police%20of%20being%20%E2%80%9Chand-in-glove%E2%80%9D%20with%20the%20complainant%20of%20the%20case.%20%E2%80%9CIn%20our%20plea%20before%20the%20SC%2C%20we%20have%20mentioned%20that%20the%20Surat%20police%20worked%20hand-in-glove%20with%20the%20complainant%20and%20arrested%20Shah.%20Following%20the%20police%20remand%2C%20he%20was%20again%20produced%20before%20the%20same%20judge%20%E2%80%93%206th%20Additional%20Chief%20Judicial%20Magistrate%20D.%20S.%20Thakar%20%E2%80%93%20who%20again%20denied%20our%20plea.%20We%20filed%20a%20fresh%20bail%20application%20and%20later%20Shah%20was%20released%2C%E2%80%9D%20added%20Syed.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20also%20wrote%20to%20Commissioner%20Ajay%20Kumar%20Tomar%20about%20the%20Vesu%20police%20working%20hand-in-glove%20with%20the%20complainant.%20Further%2C%20we%20filed%20an%20application%20with%20the%20Surat%20court%20but%20it%20was%20rejected.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20apex%20court%20issued%20notices%20to%C2%A0Gujarat%E2%80%99s%20additional%20chief%20secretary%20(home)%2C%20Surat%20Police%20commissioner%2C%20deputy%20commissioner%2C%20inspector%20of%20Vesu%20police%20station%2C%20and%20the%20additional%20chief%20judicial%20magistrate%20concerned%20and%20sought%20their%20replies%20by%20January%2029.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704971595000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F25222448%2FSupreme-Court-1.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fsc-issues-contempt-notices-to-gujarat-officials-over-police-custody-of-a-businessman%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20apex%20court%20issued%20notices%20to%20chief%20secretary%20(home)%2C%20police%20officials%2C%20and%20an%20additional%20chief%20magistrate%20over%20sending%20a%20businessman%20to%20police%20custody%20despite%20the%20top%20court%20granting%20him%20anticipatory%20bail.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fsc-issues-contempt-notices-to-gujarat-officials-over-police-custod