ee%2520people%2520have%2520reportedly%2520been%2Cthe%2520Central%2520News%2520Agency%2520reported.%5C%22%3ENews.com.au%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported.%20The%20pods%20were%20wrapped%20in%20clear%20packaging%20with%20photos%20of%20Nationalist%20Party%20candidate%20Hou%20Yu-ih%20and%20his%20running%20mate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20packages%20appeared%20to%20contain%20two%20smaller%20transparent%20packets%20containing%20red%20and%20green%20liquids%20and%20stated%20they%20could%20wash%20up%20to%20eight%20kilograms%20of%20clothes.%20It%20also%20read%3A%20%26quot%3BVote%20for%20number%20three%20as%20president%20to%20support%20you.''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20some%20people%20mistook%20the%20pods%20as%20candies%20and%20ate%20them.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThose%20hospitalised%20included%20an%2080-year-old%20man%20and%20an%2086-year-old%20woman%20who%20were%20released%20after%20having%20their%20stomachs%20flushed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHung%20Jung-chang%2C%20head%20of%20Hou's%20Chuanghua%20campaign%20office%20apologised%20for%20the%20incident%2C%20saying%20the%20office%20would%20work%20on%20%26quot%3Bdisseminating%20information%26quot%3B%20that%20the%20460%2C000%20laundry%20pods%20given%20out%20by%20the%20campaign%20were%20not%20to%20be%20eaten.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20the%20next%20wave%20of%20house-to-house%20visits%2C%20we%20will%20not%20distribute%20this%20kind%20of%20campaign%20material.%20We%20will%20also%20stress%20to%20our%20villagers%20through%20our%20grassroots%20organizations%20that%20they%20are%20laundry%20balls%2C%20not%20candies%2C''%20Mr.%20Hung%20said%20in%20a%20video%2C%20as%20per%20%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.independent.co.uk%2Fasia%2Feast-asia%2Ftaiwan-election-2024-laundry-detergent-freebie-b2476105.html%5C%22%3EIndependent.%C2%A0%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20told%20reporters%20that%20the%20campaign%20office%20staff%20would%20visit%20the%20three%20affected%20individuals%20who%20were%20hospi