%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20understand%20tipping%20is%20an%20important%20part%20of%20the%20driver%20experience%20and%20are%20proud%20that%20most%20customers%20leave%20tips%2C%20with%20the%20majority%20of%20tip%20changes%20resulting%20in%20a%20higher%20tip%20for%20drivers%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20Walmart%20spokesperson%20said.%20%26quot%3BDrivers%20keep%20100%25%20of%20confirmed%20tips.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20spokesperson%20added%3A%20%26quot%3BDriver%20feedback%20has%20been%20influential%20in%20the%20development%20of%20current%20tipping%20features%20on%20the%20platform%2C%20and%20we're%20continuously%20exploring%20new%20features%20and%20enhancements%20to%20give%20drivers%20the%20best%20possible%20experience.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EDrivers%20must%20wait%20until%20the%20next%20day%20to%20know%20what%20they%20actually%20earned%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EDozens%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgolden-age-gig-work-instacart-doordash-delivery-jobs-over-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Edelivery%20gig%20workers%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20previously%20told%20BI%20the%20job%20had%20become%20less%20profitable%20over%20the%20past%20year%2C%20increasing%20their%20reliance%20on%20tips.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Spark%20workers%20who%20spoke%20with%20BI%20said%20a%20good%20tip%20could%20make%20even%20a%20small%20order%20worth%20their%20time%20and%20expenses.%20Before%20drivers%20accept%20an%20order%2C%20the%20app%20shows%20both%20their%20base%20pay%20and%20the%20customer's%20offered%20tip.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20that%20tip%20can%20change%20over%20the%20course%20of%2024%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221632%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Walmart%2B%20Delivery%20Unlimited%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F657b51c050edbc52a8645e26%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221088%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWalmart%20Spark%20workers%20said%20a%20good%20tip%20could%20make%20even%20a%20small%20order%20worth%20their%20time%20and%20expenses.%20%3Cp%3EWalmart%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20a%20%2415%20or%20%2420%20tip%20at%20the%20time%20of%20pickup%20can%20dwindle%20to%20just%20%245%20or%20%2410%20when%20the%20transaction%20finally%20clears%2C%20a%20North%20Carolina%20Spark%20driver%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20fact%20that%20they%20make%20the%20drivers%20wait%20a%20whole%20day%20before%20we%20get%20that%20money%20%E2%80%94%20that%20is%20just%20really%20insane%20to%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDrivers%20can%20wind%20up%20making%20far%20less%20than%20they%20expected%20once%20the%2024%20hours%20is%20up%2C%20a%20Georgia%20Spark%20driver%20told%20BI.%20That's%20why%20she%20decides%20whether%20to%20take%20an%20order%20depending%20on%20its%20base%20pay%2C%20or%20the%20amount%20of%20money%20that%20Walmart%20offers%20for%20an%20order%20besides%20the%20tip.%20Another%20part%20of%20the%20calculation%20is%20how%20far%20she'll%20have%20to%20drive%20for%20the%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BGas%20is%20high%20across%20the%20country%2C%20and%20that%20pretty%20much%20means%20they%20did%20free%20work%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20driver%20said.%20%26quot%3BNobody%20should%20have%20to%20work%20for%20below%20minimum%20wage.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHer%20approach%20was%20echoed%20by%20Brock%20Dickens%2C%20a%20driver%20in%20Indiana%20who%20delivers%20for%20Spark%2C%20Amazon%2C%20and%20DoorDash.%20He%20told%20BI%20he's%20skeptical%20whenever%20he%20saw%20a%20high%20tip%20on%20an%20otherwise%20small%20order%20and%20that%20he%20wouldn't%20take%20an%20order%20unless%20the%20base%20pay%20made%20the%20order%20worth%20his%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBeing%20selective%20might%20help%20drivers%20make%20more%20money%20in%20less%20crowded%20markets%2C%20but%20that's%20less%20of%20an%20option%20in%20places%20where%20more%20drivers%20compete%20for%20fewer%20offers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20seems%20to%20be%20the%20case%20in%20parts%20of%20Oregon.%20A%20Spark%20driver%20there%20told%20BI%20his%20area%20had%20too%20many%20drivers%20and%20that%20tip%20baiting%20wasn't%20a%20significant%20problem.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20other%20words%2C%20there's%20a%20bit%20of%20a%20trade-off%3A%20Since%20tip%20baiting%20is%20generally%20a%20tactic%20customers%20use%20to%20trick%20drivers%20into%20taking%20orders%20they%20might%20otherwise%20decline%2C%20an%20oversupply%20of%20drivers%20means%20an%20order%20is%20more%20likely%20to%20be%20accepted%2C%20thus%20reducing%20the%20incentive%20for%20deception.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESpark-driver%20comments%20on%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reddit.com%2Fr%2FSparkdriver%2Fcomments%2F1803r0q%2Ftip_baiting_is_out_of_control%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EReddit%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20thread%20indicate%20that%20tip-baiting%20experiences%20vary%20widely%20but%20are%20nevertheless%20infuriating%20when%20they%20occur.%20Meanwhile%2C%20several%20drivers%20in%20the%20thread%20said%20they'd%20received%20more%20tip%20increases%20than%20decreases.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20driver%20in%20Detroit%20told%20BI%20a%20friend%20of%20his%20saw%20his%20tips%20reduced%20two%20to%20three%20times%20a%20month%2C%20but%2C%20as%20Walmart%20pointed%20out%2C%20Spark's%20adjustment%20feature%20goes%20both%20ways.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20only%20time%20I've%20had%20a%20customer%20change%20their%20tip%20is%20to%20give%20me%20more%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20driver%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EDo%20you%20work%20for%20Spark%20and%20have%20a%20story%20idea%20to%20share%3F%20Reach%20out%20to%20these%20reporters%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Aabitter%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3Eabitter%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20and%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Adreuter%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3Edreuter%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2F