20this%20annual%20gathering%20of%20investors%20was%20a%20%26quot%3Bgreat%20platform%20to%20reassert%20our%20business%20to%20business%20and%20people%20to%20people%20ties.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20relations%20between%20the%20two%20countries%20saw%20some%20bitterness%20last%20year%20following%20Canadian%20Prime%20Minister%20Justin%20Trudeau's%20allegation%20about%20India's%20suspected%20involvement%20in%20the%20killing%20of%20Khalistani%20separatist%20and%20designated%20terrorist%20Hardeep%20Singh%20Nijjar%20in%20his%20country.%20India%20denied%20the%20allegation%20as%20absurd.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20the%20past%20months%2C%20it%20has%20been%20a%20time%20of%20some%20tensions%20between%20our%20two%20countries.%20It%20is%20no%20secret.%20But%20I%20am%20encouraged%20by%20leadership%20and%20vision%20of%20business%20community%20present%20here%20and%20outside%20the%20room%20to%20continue%20with%20trade%20and%20investment%20relationship%20which%20is%20in%20the%20interest%20of%20both%20of%20our%20countries%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Mackay%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20business-to-business%20ties%20will%20support%20job%20creation%2C%20technology%20partnership%20and%20prosperity%20of%20both%20the%20countries%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20advice%20to%20my%20government%20and%20that%20to%20the%20Indian%20government%20and%20business%20community%20on%20both%20sides%20is%20to%20let%20the%20governments%20do%20what%20they%20are%20doing%2C%20let%20the%20government%20do%20diplomacy%20but%20everyone%20knows%20that%20in%20the%20long%20term%2C%20Canada's%20strategic%20interest%20and%20India's%20strategic%20interest%20are%20absolutely%20aligned%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20high%20commissioner%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20the%20meantime%20let's%20have%20business%20to%20business%20ties.%20We%20should%20work%20together%20to%20make%20our%20business%20and%20nations%20friendly%20again%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBusiness%20relations