le%20the%20impact%20on%20metal%20output%20if%20production%20of%20automobiles%20slows.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ETrade%20shocks%20are%20assessed%20using%20the%20WTO%20Global%20Trade%20Model%20(GTM)%20(Aguiar%20et%20al%2C%202019).%20The%20GTM%20is%20a%20recursive%20computational%20general%20equilibrium%20model%20based%20on%20the%20GTAP%20model%20(version%207)%20(Corong%20et%20al%2C%202017).%20We%20shock%20tariffs%20and%20non%20tariff%20measures%2C%20including%20as%20a%20proxy%20for%20sanctions%20and%20export%20controls.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EUS%20allies%20are%20defined%20based%20on%20trade%20shares%2C%20treaty%20relationships%2C%20and%20Bloomberg%20Economics'%20judgement.%20Australia%2C%20Canada%2C%20the%20European%20Free%20Trade%20Association%2C%20the%20European%20Union%2C%20Japan%2C%20Mexico%2C%20South%20Korea%20and%20the%20UK%20are%20defined%20as%20US%20allies.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EFinancial%20shock%20impacts%20are%20estimated%20following%20a%20structural%20approach%20based%20on%20the%20Bayesian%20Global%20VAR%20model%20(Bock%2C%20Feldkircher%20and%20Huber%2C%202020).%20The%20model%20is%20amended%20slightly%20by%20adding%20log%20real%20equity%20prices%20for%20each%20country%20as%20in%20Mohaddes%20and%20Raissi%20(2020).%20Uncertainty%20in%20the%20financial%20markets%20is%20modeled%20as%20a%20global%20shock%20to%20the%20VIX.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EA%20key%20uncertainty%20in%20the%20analysis%20is%20the%20extent%20to%20which%20missing%20semiconductor%20output%20from%20Taiwan%20could%20be%20replaced%20by%20output%20in%20other%20locations%2C%20worked%20around%20by%20manufacturing%20firms%2C%20or%20backstopped%20from%20inventories.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Bloomberg%20Economics%20scenarios%20assume%20that%20all%20production%20using%20semiconductors%20as%20inputs%20has%20to%20be%20reduced%20in%20line%20with%20the%20reduction%20in%20semiconductors%20availability%3A%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E-For%20advanced%20electronics%20such%20as%20smartphones%20using%20cutting-edge%20logic%20chips%2C%20this%20translates%20into%20a%2060%25%20reduction%20in%20production%20in%20the%20blockade%20scenario%2C%20rising%20to%2085%25%20in%20the%20war%20scenario%20when%20access%20to%20South%20Korean%20production%20is%20also%20severely%20curtailed.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn-For%20sectors%20using%20lagging-edge%20logic%20chips%2C%20like%20those%20used%20in%20autos%20and%20home%20electronics%2C%20that%20means%2035%25%20in%20the%20blockade%20scenario%20when%20Taiwan's%20output%20goes%20offline%2C%20and%2062%25%20in%20the%20war%20scenario%20when%20output%20from%20China%2C%20Japan%2C%20and%20South%20Korea%20is%20also%20lost.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EReality%20could%20end%20up%20being%20better.%20For%20example%2C%20other%20countries%20could%20amp%20up%20chip%20production%2C%20or%20auto%20firms%20and%20other%20manufacturers%20might%20find%20work%20arounds%20for%20missing%20inputs.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EIt%20could%20also%20be%20worse.%20For%20example%2C%20if%20Taiwan's%20chips%20are%20not%20replaceable%20and%20use%20of%20them%20is%20distributed%20widely%20across%20products.%20If%20production%20for%20all%20sectors%20using%20leading%20and%20lagging%20edge%20chips%20goes%20to%20zero%2C%20the%20blow%20to%20global%20GDP%20in%20the%20war%20scenario%20increases%20from%2010.2%25%20to%2014%25.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704966420000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2F4j1ctpb4_taiwan-bloomberg_625x300_11_January_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fxi-jinping-joe-biden-and-the-10-trillion-cost-of-war-over-taiwan-4841869%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22War%20over%20Taiwan%20would%20have%20a%20cost%20in%20blood%20and%20treasure%20so%20vast%20that%20even%20those%20unhappiest%20with%20the%20status%20quo%20have%20reason%20not%20to%20risk%20it.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fxi-jinping-joe-biden-and-the-10-trillion-cost-of-war-over-taiwan-4841869%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fxi-jinping-joe-biden-and-the-10-trillion-cost-of-war-over-taiwan-4841869%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fxi-jinping-joe-biden-and-the-10-trillion-cost-of-war-over-taiwan-4841869%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Biren%20Singh%20Opening%20a%20New%20Front'%3A%20Manipur%20Govt's%20Possible%20Rethink%20on%20ST%20Status%20to%20Kukis%20Draws%20Ire%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F30163218%2FFwqAt6VXsAIGp1_.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EEven%20as%20violence%20continues%20to%20rage%20in%20Manipur%2C%20Kuki-Zomi%20organisations%20have%20accused%20the%20state%20government%20under%20chief%20minister%20N.%20Biren%20Singh%20of%20%E2%80%9Copening%20a%20new%20front%E2%80%9D%20in%20the%20ongoing%20violence%20after%20Singh%20said%20that%20his%20government%20is%20considering%20setting%20up%20a%20committee%20to%20rethink%20the%20Scheduled%20Tribe%20status%20of%20the%20Kukis%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3EIndian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fpolitical-pulse%2Fkukis-cm-biren-singh-new-front-escalate-conflict-govt-rethink-st-status-9103934%2F%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAny%20such%20attempts%20to%20%E2%80%9Cuse%20the%20state%20machinery%20to%20target%E2%80%9D%20their%20community%20will%20further%20escalate%20the%20conflict%2C%20they%20warned.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESingh%E2%80%99s%20statement%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20January%209%2C%20came%20in%20response%20to%20queries%20on%20a%20representation%20made%20to%20the%20Union%20ministry%20of%20tribal%20affairs%20by%20the%20Meitei%20leader%20of%20the%20Republican%20Party%20of%20India%20(Athawale)%2C%20Maheshwar%20Thounaojam%2C%20for%20the%20exclusion%20of%20Kukis%20from%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20ST%20list.%20Thounaojam%20holds%20the%20view%20that%20%E2%80%9Cthey%20(Kukis)%20are%20not%20the%20original%20inhabitants%20of%20Manipur%E2%80%9D.%20The%20Centre%20forwarded%20the%20representation%20to%20the%20state%20government%2C%20as%20the%20latter%E2%80%99s%20recommendation%20is%C2%A0a%20prerequisite%20to%20process%20any%20such%20proposal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESingh%20said%20that%20an%20all-tribe%20committee%20would%20be%20formed%20to%20decide%20whether%20the%20Chin%20Kuki%20community%20would%20be%20deleted%20from%20the%20Scheduled%20Tribes%20list%20of%20the%20state.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20were%20included%20in%20the%20(ST)%20list%20of%20Manipur%20but%20how%20they%20were%20included%20needs%20to%20be%20re-examined.%20Before%20commenting%2C%20we%20have%20to%20form%20a%20committee%20consisting%20of%20all%20tribes%20(of%20the%20state)%2C%E2%80%9D%20Singh%20told%20reporters%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fother-states%2Fall-tribe-panel-to-be-formed-to-decide-if-chin-kukis-will-remain-st-manipur-cm%2Farticle67724832.ece%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20Press%20Trust%20of%20India%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKuki%20is%20a%20collective%20name%20of%20various%20tribes%20of%20Manipur%2C%20and%20Chin%20is%20one%20of%20those.%20The%20Chin%20community%20people%20also%20share%20ethnicity%20with%20the%20Mizos%20of%20Mizoram%20and%20a%20section%20of%20the%20residents%20of%20neighbouring%20Myanmar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETaking%20exception%20to%20Singh%E2%80%99s%20remarks%2C%20Indigenous%20Tribal%20Leaders%E2%80%99%20Forum%20(ITLF)%2C%20a%20Kuki-Zomi%20organisation%20based%20in%20Churachandpur%2C%20accused%20%E2%80%9Ccommunal%E2%80%9D%20Biren%20Singh%20of%20%E2%80%9Copening%20a%20new%20front%E2%80%9D.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20no%20secret%20that%20the%20state%20government%20in%20Manipur%2C%20controlled%20by%20the%20majority%20Meitei%20community%2C%20overtly%20and%20covertly%20supports%20the%20Meiteis%20in%20the%20current%20ethnic%20conflict.%20The%20communal%20Biren%20Singh%20administration%20has%20now%20opened%20a%20new%20front%20by%20pushing%20for%20the%20removal%20of%20the%20Kuki-Zo%20community%20from%20India%E2%80%99s%20ST%20list%2C%E2%80%9D%20read%20a%20statement%20issued%20by%20the%20ITLF%20on%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAny%20further%20attempts%20by%20Biren%20Singh%20to%20use%20the%20state%20machinery%20to%20target%20the%20Kuki-Zo%20community%20will%20only%20escalate%20the%20conflict%2C%20which%20will%20ultimately%20be%20detrimental%20to%20him%20and%20the%20state%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20statement%20further%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKuki%20Inpi%2C%20the%20apex%20body%20of%20Kuki%20tribes%20in%20Manipur%2C%20called%20on%20the%20state%20government%20to%20stop%20any%20attempts%20to%20%E2%80%9Calter%20the%20ST%20status%20of%20the%20community%E2%80%9D%20immediately.%20%E2%80%9CKuki%20Inpi%20Sadar%20Hills%20vehemently%20condemns%20any%20attempt%20to%20erase%20the%20Kuki%20community%20from%20Scheduled%20Tribe%20status%2C%20as%20it%20blatantly%20violates%20the%20principles%20enshrined%20in%20the%20Indian%20Constitution.%20Such%20actions%20not%20only%20undermine%20the%20Constitutional%20safeguards%20provided%20to%20tribal%20communities%20but%20also%20perpetuate%20injustice%20and%20discrimination%2C%E2%80%9D%20Kuki%20Inpi%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EManipur%20has%20been%20rocked%20by%20ethnic%20violence%20since%20May%20last%20year%20and%20over%20180%20people%20were%20killed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20violence%20erupted%20on%20May%203%20after%20a%20%E2%80%98Tribal%20Solidarity%20March%E2%80%99%20was%20organised%20in%20the%20hill%20districts%20to%20protest%20against%20the%20Meitei%20community%E2%80%99s%20demand%20for%20Scheduled%20Tribe%20(ST)%20status.%C2%A0Meiteis%20account%20for%20about%2053%25%20of%20Manipur%E2%80%99s%20population%20and%20live%20mostly%20in%20the%