Paid%2030%2C000%20For%20Cab%26quot%3B%3A%20Goa%20Hotel%20Manager%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EDesperate%20to%20hide%20the%20fact%20that%20she%20was%20carrying%20her%20son's%20body%20stuffed%20in%20one%20of%20her%20bags%2C%20the%20CEO%20accused%20of%20killing%20him%20chose%20to%20pay%20Rs%2030%2C000%20for%20a%20cab%20from%20Goa%20to%20Bengaluru.%20This%20has%20been%20revealed%20in%20the%20police%20complaint%20filed%20by%20the%20manager%20of%20the%20serviced%20apartment%20in%20Goa%2C%20where%20Suchana%20Seth%20allegedly%20killed%20her%20four-year-old%20son.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20complaint%20says%20that%20the%20staff%20members%20at%20the%20serviced%20apartment%20pointed%20out%20to%20Seth%20that%20taking%20a%20flight%20would%20be%20much%20cheaper%2C%20but%20she%20%26quot%3Binsisted%26quot%3B%20on%20travelling%20in%20a%20cab.%20A%20search%20on%20flight%20booking%20websites%20reveals%20that%20even%20last-minute%20tickets%20from%20Goa%20to%20Bengaluru%20are%20available%20for%20between%20Rs%202%2C600%20and%20Rs%203%2C000%20per%20passenger.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20manager%20also%20said%20that%20Seth%20had%20booked%20the%20room%20from%20January%206%20to%20January%2010%20-%20and%20had%20paid%20for%20it%20in%20advance%20-%20but%20checked%20out%20at%2012.30%20am%20on%20January%208.%20The%20complaint%20was%20filed%20later%20the%20same%20day.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeth%2C%20who%20is%20now%20in%20police%20custody%20for%20the%20alleged%20murder%2C%20is%20the%20CEO%20of%20Mindful%20AI%20Lab%20and%20claims%20that%20she%20is%20an%20%26quot%3Bartificial%20intelligence%20ethics%20expert%26quot%3B%20on%20her%20LinkedIn%20profile%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECough%20Syrup%20Request%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EListing%20out%20the%20sequence%20of%20events%20in%20his%20complaint%20in%20the%20Calangute%20police%20station%2C%20Gagan%20Gambhir%2C%20the%20manager%20of%20the%20Sol%20Banyan%20Grande%20serviced%20apartment%20in%20Candolim%2C%20said%20Seth%20and%20her%20four-year-old%20son%20had%20checked%20in%20on%20the%20night%20of%20January%206%20and%20were%20staying%20in%20Room%20404.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbengaluru-ceo-suchana-seth-accused-of-killing-son-asked-husband-to-meet-child-day-before-murder-4840217%5C%22%3ECEO%20Accused%20Of%20Killing%20Son%20Texted%20Husband%20The%20Day%20She%20Checked%20Into%20Goa%20Hotel%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Gambhir%20states%20that%2C%20around%204%20pm%20the%20next%20day%2C%20Seth%20made%20a%20call%20to%20the%20reception%20and%20said%20she%20needed%20two%20bottles%20of%20cough%20syrup%20from%20a%20particular%20brand.%20The%20CEO%20said%20the%20bottles%20of%20cough%20syrup%20were%20for%20her%2C%20and%20they%20were%20handed%20over%20to%20her%20by%20a%20staff%20member.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20angles%20being%20investigated%20by%20the%20police%20is%20whether%20Seth%20drugged%20her%20son%20using%20cough%20syrup%20and%20then%20smothered%20him%20with%20a%20pillow.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFive%20hours%20later%2C%20at%209.10%20pm%2C%20Seth%20informed%20the%20staff%20at%20the%20serviced%20apartment%20that%20she%20had%20some%20urgent%20work%20in%20Bengaluru%20and%20asked%20them%20to%20book%20a%20cab%20for%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECheaper%20Option%20Rejected%2C%20Bloodstains%20Found%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20at%20this%20point%20that%20the%20staff%20members%20told%20her%20that%20taking%20a%20flight%20would%20be%20cheaper.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20reception%20staff%20informed%20her%20that%20flight%20tickets%20are%20cheaper%20than%20hiring%20a%20taxi%20but%20she%20insisted%20for%20taxi.%20Accordingly%2C%20we%20had%20arranged%20one%20Innova%20Crysta...%20driven%20by%20one%20Rayjohn...%20for%20a%20fare%20of%20Rs.%2030%2C000%2F-.%20She%20agreed%20for%20the%20same%20and%20on%20arrival%20of%20taxi%2C%20said%20lady%20checked%20out%20at%20around%2000.30%20hours%20on%2008%2F01%2F2024%20and%20after%20loading%20her%20luggage%20in%20taxi%20she%20left%20from%20the%20service%20apartment%20(sic)%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20complaint%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20few%20hours%20later%2C%20while%20cleaning%20the%20room%2C%20a%20member%20of%20the%20housekeeping%20staff%20noticed%20bloodstains%20and%20informed%20Mr%20Gambhir%2C%20who%20alerted%20the%20police%20control%20room.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20complaint%20states%20that%20some%20police%20officials%20visited%20Sol%20Banyan%20Grande%20and%20inspected%20Room%20404%2C%20where%20they%20%26quot%3Bnoticed%20bloodstains%20in%20the%20living%20room%2C%20bedroom%20and%20bathroom%26quot%3B.%20They%20also%20spoke%20to%20the%20watchman%2C%20who%20confirmed%20that%20Seth%20had%20left%20alone.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFake%20Address%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20called%20up%20the%20cab%20driver%2C%20requested%20him%20to%20pass%20the%20phone%20to%20Seth%20and%20asked%20her%20where%20her%20son%20was.%20The%20complaint%20states%20the%20CEO%20said%20he%20was%20staying%20with%20one%20of%20her%20friends%20in%20Goa's%20Margao%20and%20she%20was%20asked%20to%20send%20the%20address.%20A%20police%20inspector%20of%20Calangute%20police%20station%20asked%20his%20counterpart%20in%20Fatorda%20to%20verify%20the%20address%2C%20which%20was%20found%20to%20be%20fake.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsuchana-seth-bengaluru-ceo-goa-child-murder-how-an-accident-on-goa-border-led-police-to-ceo-who-killed-her-child-4837044%5C%22%3EHow%20An%20Accident%20On%20Goa%20Border%20Led%20Police%20To%20Bengaluru%20CEO%20Who%20Killed%20Her%20Child%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Calangute%20police%20inspector%20then%20called%20Royjohn%20and%20ordered%20him%20to%20drive%20to%20the%20nearest%20police%20station%20and%20ask%20officials%20there%20to%20check%20Seth's%20luggage.%20The%20dr