3A%2F%2Fwww.brunswickgroup.com%2Feight-key-elections-to-watch-in-2024-i25831%2F%5C%22%3Eworldwide%20wave%20of%20elections%3C%2Fa%3E.%20States%20representing%20billions%20of%20people%20and%20around%2050%25%20of%20world%20GDP%20are%20going%20to%20the%20polls%20this%20year.%20Many%20states%20face%20potentially%20volatile%20election%20processes%20in%20geopolitically%20fraught%20times%2C%20as%20well%20as%20with%20widespread%20domestic%20volatility%20%E2%80%93%20UK%2C%20Taiwan%2C%20India%2C%20UK%2C%20European%20Union%2C%20Indonesia%2C%20Russia%2C%20South%20Africa%2C%20among%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeveral%20of%20those%20global%20elections%20%E2%80%93%20UK%2C%20EU%2C%20South%20Africa%2C%20India%2C%20Taiwan%20%E2%80%93%20have%20a%20direct%20impact%20or%20at%20least%20implications%20for%20the%20US%2C%20especially%20regarding%20geopolitical%20rivalries%20(attitudes%20to%20the%20Ukraine%20war%20and%20military%20aid%20for%20example%3B%20Taiwan%E2%80%99s%20posture%20towards%20Beijing%20and%20the%20US%3B%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20war%20on%20Gaza%20and%20the%20politics%20of%20a%20ceasefire%20resolution)%2C%20and%20the%20prospects%20for%20international%20economic%20coordination.%20The%20war%20in%20Ukraine%20and%20the%20fear%20of%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20onslaught%20on%20the%20people%20of%20Gaza%20spiralling%20into%20a%20regional%20war%2C%20impact%20and%20implicate%20the%20United%20States%2C%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20regional%20power.%20The%20only%20superpower%20that%20is%20virtually%20omnipresent%2C%20to%20which%20everywhere%20is%20a%20national%20interest.%20The%20privileges%20of%20full%20spectrum%20dominance%20and%20forward%20power%20projection.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20implications%20for%20President%20Biden%E2%80%99s%20re-election%20bid%20are%20increasingly%20bleak%20as%20national%20polls%20show%20Trump%20leading%20the%20incumbent%2C%20and%20as%20Arab%20and%20Muslim-Americans%20develop%20campaigns%20against%20the%20administration%E2%80%99s%20support%20for%20Israel%20and%20blocking%20of%20a%20ceasefire%20resolution%20at%20the%20United%20Nations.%20Though%20they%20are%20a%20very%20small%20minority%20of%20the%20US%20population%20and%20electorate%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthehill.com%2Fhomenews%2Fcampaign%2F4356645-arab-muslim-americans-could-abandon-biden-democrats-warn-advocates%2F%5C%22%3EMuslim-Americans%3C%2Fa%3E%20could%20tilt%20the%20balance%20of%20power%20within%20swing%20states%20towards%20Donald%20Trump.%20As%20ominously%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.brookings.edu%2Farticles%2Ffor-biden-youth-vote-polling-is-a-warning-not-the-apocalypse%2F%5C%22%3Evoters%20under%2035%20years%20of%20age%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20much%20larger%20slice%20of%20the%20electorate%2C%20who%20supported%20Biden%20by%20large%20margins%20in%202020%2C%20seem%20to%20be%20deserting%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20984px)%2061vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2045vw%2C%20600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F04%2F08132647%2Fdownload-3.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22800%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F04%2F08132647%2Fdownload-3.jpg%20800w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F04%2F08132647%2Fdownload-3-300x200.jpg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-521330%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22533%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ETrump%20supporters%20marching%20on%20the%20US%20Capitol%20on%206%20January%202021.%20Photo%3A%20Wikimedia%20Commons.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBut%20America%20remains%20great%E2%80%A6.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYet%20there%20remains%20an%20incontrovertible%20and%20fundamental%20fact%3A%20that%20while%20worldwide%20elections%20are%20important%2C%20their%20impacts%20are%20largely%20confined%20to%20specific%20regions%20or%20domains.%20The%20US%20election%2C%20however%2C%20is%20pivotal%20on%20all%20fronts%20%E2%80%93%20geoeconomically%2C%20geopolitically%2C%20politically%20%E2%80%93%20with%20worldwide%20ramifications.%20For%20all%20the%20talk%20of%20%E2%80%98decline%E2%80%99%20or%20the%20transition%20to%20multipolarity%2C%20the%20US%20remains%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20pivotal%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20fundamental%20issues%20for%20the%20United%20States%20are%20domestically-rooted%20%E2%80%93%20in%20its%20politics%2C%20political%20system%2C%20and%20political%20economy.%20Factionalisation%20is%20the%20core%20political%20problem%3B%20a%20political%20party%20system%20deeply%20divided%2C%20political%20violence%20at%20enduringly%20high%20levels%2C%20an%20indicted%20GOP%20candidate%20leading%20a%20party%20uncommitted%20to%20free%20and%20fair%20elections%20and%20rules%20of%20the%20game%3B%20social%20and%20economic%20inequalities%2C%20and%20polarisations.%20And%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.americanprogress.org%2Farticle%2Fcorporate-capture-threatens-democratic-government%2F%5C%22%3Ecorporate%20dominance%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20both%20parties%20and%20their%20political-economic%20agendas%20remains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecent%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.harvard.edu%2Fgazette%2Fstory%2F2022%2F08%2Ftop-business-execs-more-polarized-than-nation-as-whole%2F%5C%22%3Eresearch%3C%2Fa%3E%20also%20shows%20that%20the%20top%20executives%20of%20major%20US%20corporations%20are%20leaning%20even%20more%20heavily%20toward%20the%20GOP%2C%20even%20as%20they%20mouth%20slogans%20about%20diversity%20and%20face%20accusations%20of%20%E2%80%9Cwokism%E2%80%9D%20from%20the%20Right.%20The%20corporate%20constituency%20behind%20a%20fascistic%20Trump-led%20political%20party%20has%20grown.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20the%20reasons%20are%20not%20hard%20to%20find.%20When%20asked%20recently%20if%20he%20would%20be%20a%20dictator%20were%20he%20returned%20to%20the%20White%20House%2C%20Trump%20replied%20that%20he%20would%20be%20for%20just%20one%20day.%20On%20that%20day%2C%20he%20would%20close%20the%20borders%20and%2C%20very%20significantly%2C%20abolish%20government%20regulation%20of%20fossil%20fuel%20corporations.%20Racist%20divide%20and%20rule%20twinned%20with%20corporate%20freedom%20%E2%80%93%20the%20core%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Fus-news%2F2023%2Fdec%2F06%2Fdonald-trump-sean-hannity-dictator-day-one-response-iowa-town-hall%5C%22%3ETrump%E2%80%99s%20political%20strategy%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fus-fascistic-violence-civil-war-election-2024%5C%22%3Etoxic%20recipe%20for%20political%20strife%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20violence%2C%20far-right%20and%20fascistic%20extremism%2C%20and%20state%20repression%20against%20popular%20resistance.%20Discussion%2C%20fearful%20and%20shocking%2C%20about%20fascism%20and%20civil%20war%20is%20now%20common%2C%20even%20if%20the%20mainstream%20media%20does%20not%20recognise%20it%2C%20as%20Bill%20Clinton%E2%80%99s%20labour%20secretary%20Robert%20Reich%2C%20recently%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Fcommentisfree%2F2023%2Fdec%2F31%2Fmainstream-media-is-playing-into-trumps-neo-fascist-hands-im-sticking-with-democracy-and-the-guardian%5C%22%3Eclaimed%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBarbara%20F%20Walter%E2%80%99s%20important%20study%20%E2%80%93%20%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbooks%2Fbook-review-barbara-walter-america-civil-war-fascism%5C%22%3EHow%20Civil%20Wars%20Start%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%20(2022)%20%E2%80%93%20remains%20the%20key%20reference%20point%20with%20regard%20to%20the%20%E2%80%9Cfactionalisation%E2%80%9D%20process%20and%20the%20road%20to%20civil%20war%20and%20political%20violence%3A%20it%20remains%20relevant%20to%20understanding%20US%20politics%20today%20including%20the%20path%20to%20the%202024%20election%20and%20its%20ramifications%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECrises%20galore%20%E2%80%93%20poly%2C%20perma%2C%20organic%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20a%20fundamental%20legitimacy%20crisis%20%E2%80%93%20a%20crisis%20of%20authority%20of%20the%20two%20main%20parties%20and%20their%20leaders%20%E2%80%93%20which%20remains%20the%20core%20underlying%20bedrock%20problem.%20It%20is%20the%20motherlode%20from%20which%20emanates%20all%20other%20schisms%20and%20faultlines.%20Call%20it%20what%20you%20will%20and%20from%20whichever%20part%20of%20the%20ideological%20spectrum%20%E2%80%93%20poly%20crisis%2C%20perma%20crisis%2C%20organic%20crisis%20%E2%80%93%20crisis%20is%20now%20part%20of%20the%20lexicon%20of%20our%20times.%20The%20new%20normal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20crisis%20has%20a%20face%20%E2%80%93%20two%20faces%2C%20actually%2C%20as%20exemplified%20by%20the%20two%20likely%20main%20contenders%20for%20the%20US%20presidency%3A%20Donald%20Trump%20and%20Joseph%20Biden%2C%20in%20a%20country%20seen%20by%20the%20majority%20of%20voters%20as%20heading%20in%20the%20wrong%20direction.%20Trump%E2%80%99s%20age%2C%20criminal%20indictments%20(and%20two%20impeachments)%20and%20march%20towards%20American-style%20fascism%3B%20and%20Biden%E2%80%99s%20age%20and%20health%2C%20and%20foot-dragging%20on%20indictments%20of%20Trump%20since%202021.%20Major%20complicating%20issues.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20mere%20eight%20swing%20states%20may%20determine%20the%20election%20outcome%20%E2%80%93%20Arizona%2C%20Michigan%2C%20Georgia%2C%20Wisconsin%2C%20Pennsylvania%2C%20New%20Hampshire%2C%20and%20North%20Carolina%20%E2%80%93%20another%20tight%20race%20between%20two%20unpopular%20candidates.%20If%20there%20were%20such%20a%20choice%20in%202024%2C%20%E2%80%9C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FNone_of_the_above%5C%22%3ENone%20of%20the%20Above%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%9D%20would%20win%20the%20election.%20The%20lesser%20of%20two%20evils%20or%20the%20evil%20of%20two%20lessers%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Trump%E2%80%99s%20name%20on%20ballots%20in%20several%20states%20is%20in%20jeopardy%20or%20removed.%20The%20matter%20will%20end%20up%20at%20the%20door%20of%20the%20right-wing%20majority%20US%20Supreme%20Court.%20Another%20first%20for%20Donald%20Trump.%20Whichever%20way%20the%20chips%20fall%20%E2%80%93%20most%20likely%20towards%20Trump%20and%20his%20incensed%20fan%20base%20%E2%80%93%20political%20peace%20is%20unlikely%20to%20prevail%20in%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fwill-the-sc-rule-in-trumps-favour-to-keep-his-presidential-ambitions-alive%5C%22%3EWill%20the%20SC%20Rule%20in%20Trump%E2%80%99s%20Favour%20to%20Keep%20His%20Presidential%20Ambitions%20Alive%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20will%20need%20to%20keep%20an%20eye%20on%20setting%20a%20precedent%20when%20it%20rules%20on%20barring%20Trump%20from%20the%202024%20election.%20If%20Trump%20is%20ruled%20to%20be%20exempt%20from%20the%2014%3Cspan%3Eth%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Amendment%E2%80%99s%20Article%203%2C%20which%20bars%20insurrectionists%20from%20holding%20office%20if%20they%20have%20taken%20an%20oath%20to%20protect%20and%20uphold%20the%20Constitution%2C%20there%20would%20be%20wider%20ramifications.%20The%20right-wing%20majority%20Supreme%20Court%20would%20also%20be%20giving%20virtual%20carte%20blanche%20to%20any%20future%20president%20of%20a%20political%20persuasion%20uncongenial%20to%20the%20GOP%20to%20refuse%20to%20leave%20office%20following%20electoral%20defeat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%20laughable%20the%20notion%20that%20a%20US%20president%20is%20not%20an%20officer%20of%20the%20United%20States%2C%20this%20is%20the%20main%20plank%20of%20Trump%E2%80%99s%20case.%20And%20the%20claim%20that%20barring%20him%20for%20insurrection%20is%20anti-democratic%20reinforces%20the%20upside%20down%20logics%20of%20American%20political%20culture%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWill%20there%20be%20a%20peaceful%20transfer%20of%20power%3F%20There%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20one%20in%202020.%20Thousands%20of%20politically%20vetted%20national%20guard%20were%20on%20duty%20during%20Biden%E2%80%99s%20inauguration.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECould%20the%20US%20break%20up%20along%20political%20lines%20with%20some%20states%20accepting%20and%20others%20rejecting%20the%20outcome%3F%20Who%20knows%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20these%20questions%20are%20being%20asked%20at%20all%20is%20an%20indication%20of%20the%20new%20reality%20of%20the%20US%20and%20therefore%20global%20political%20life%2C%20of%20the%20global%20disorder.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fauthor%2Fiparmar%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EInderjeet%20Parmar%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20is%20a%20professor%20of%20international%20politics%20and%20associate%20dean%20of%20research%20in%20the%20School%20of%20Policy%20and%20Global%20Affairs%20at%20City%2C%20University%20of%20London%2C%20a%20fellow%20of%20the%20Academy%20of%20Social%20Sciences%2C%20and%20a%20columnist%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3EThe%20Wire%3Cem%3E.%20He%20is%20an%20International%20Fellow%20at%20the%20ROADS%20Initiative%20think%20tank%2C%20Islamabad%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3Eand%20author%20of%20several%20books%20including%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3EFoundations%20of%20the%20American%20Century%3Cem%3E.%20He%20is%20currently%20writing%20a%20book%20on%20the%20history%2C%20politics%2C%20and%20powers%20of%20the%20US%20Foreign%20Policy%20Establishment.%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704963601000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F11140034%2FEffect-61.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fas-the-us-enters-election-year-will-there-be-a-peaceful-transfer-of-power%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22There%20is%20a%20deep%20sense%20of%20foreboding%20in%20the%20US%20as%20the%20implications%20for%20President%20Biden's%20re-election%20bid%20are%20increasingly%20bleak%20as%20national%20polls%20show%20Trump%20leading%20the%20incumbent.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22enga