ted%20by%20Abhishek%20Chaubey.%20%C2%A0The%20owners%20of%20the%20phones%20are%20dead%20but%20the%20warped%20connection%20lingers%20on%20and%20impacts%20the%20course%20of%20the%20insanely%20twisted%20eight-episode%20Netflix%20series.%20The%20freakish%20is%20par%20for%20the%20course%20here.%20As%20more%20people%20die%2C%20each%20life%20lost%20casts%20a%20shadow%2C%20literally%20and%20figuratively%2C%20on%20those%20that%20survive.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20Latin%20sign%20outside%20a%20mortuary%20in%20the%20fictional%20Tamil%20Nadu%20hill%20town%20that%20%3Cem%3EKiller%20Soup%3C%2Fem%3E%20is%20set%20in%20reads%20%26quot%3BMortui%20vivos%20docent%26quot%3B%20(%26quot%3Bthe%20dead%20teach%20the%20living%26quot%3B).%20The%20living%20learn%20little%20in%20this%20neck%20of%20the%20woods.%20They%20frantically%20try%20-%20and%20fail%20-%20to%20shrug%20off%20the%20burden%20of%20the%20departed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EKiller%20Soup%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20a%20deftly%20crafted%20crime%20and%20investigation%20caper%20marked%20by%20whip-smart%20writing%20and%20unerring%20acting%2C%20is%20quirky%2C%20sly%20and%20hugely%20entertaining.%20One%20of%20its%20two%20principal%20characters%20is%20Swathi%20Shetty%20(Konkona%20Sen%20Sharma)%2C%20an%20inept%20cook%20who%20hopes%20to%20start%20a%20restaurant%20of%20her%20own.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20self-absorbed%20husband%2C%20Prabhakar%20'Prabhu'%20Shetty%20(Manoj%20Bajpayee)%2C%20promises%20to%20help%20her%20but%20is%20more%20interested%20in%20pulling%20himself%20out%20of%20a%20hole%20after%20having%20botched%20up%20several%20business%20projects.%20Their%20marriage%20is%20a%20recipe%20for%20disaster.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrabhu's%20foulmouthed%20elder%20brother%2C%20Arvind%20Shetty%20(Sayaji%20Shinde)%2C%20wavers%20between%20fraternal%20affection%20and%20corrosive%20candour.%20He%20loses%20no%20opportunity%20to%20tick%20Prabhu%20off%20for%20his%20profligacies.%20Prabhu%20shamelessly%20leeches%20off%20his%20big%20brother.%20The%20latter%2C%20too%2C%20has%20skeletons%20aplenty%20in%20the%20closet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESwathi%2C%20disgruntled%20as%20much%20with%20what%20she%20lacks%20as%20with%20what%20she%20possesses%2C%20has%20an%20affair%20with%20a%20masseur%2C%20Umesh%20Pillai%20(Bajpayee%20in%20a%20dual%20role)%2C%20who%20serves%20the%20Shetty%20brothers%20and%20knows%20a%20great%20deal%20about%20their%20shady%20business%20practices.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FGa0XeUKWTys%3Fsi%3DXF50o9P5m0eBnhxS%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20lid%20is%20blown%20off%20their%20liaison%2C%20Swathi%20and%20Umesh%20panic.%20A%20string%20of%20ill-advised%20moves%20lands%20them%20in%20a%20soup.%20A%20sudden%20death%2C%20a%20pell-mell%20cover-up%20and%20a%20grotesque%20facial%20reconstruction%20later%2C%20their%20lies%2C%20betrayal%20and%20deception%20assume%20near-diabolical%20proportions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChaubey%2C%20in%20concert%20with%20co-writers%20and%20creators%20Anaiza%20Merchant%2C%20Anant%20Tripathi%20and%20Harshad%20Nalawade%2C%20rustles%20up%20a%20gripping%2C%20darkly%20comic%20crime%20drama%20that%20knows%20exactly%20where%20it%20is%20headed%20but%20succeeds%20in%20keeping%20the%20audience%20on%20tenterhooks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELike%20Chaubey's%20films%2C%20the%20series%20is%20rooted%20in%20a%20defined%2C%20immersive%2C%20authentic%20space.%20The%20soundtrack%20is%2C%20however%2C%20a%20medley%20of%20languages%20and%20dialects%20spoken%20with%20a%20variety%20of%20accents.%20The%20range%20of%20linguistic%20peculiarities%20and%20cadences%20significantly%20enrich%20the%20show.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETamil%2C%20Malayalam%20and%20Dakhini%20liberally%20punctuate%20the%20assortment%20of%20Hindi%20and%20English%20dictions%20that%20are%20strewn%20across%20the%20series.%20Add%20to%20that%20mix%20Robert%20Frost's%20%26quot%3BThe%20woods%20are%20lovely%2C%20dark%20and%20deep%26quot%3B%20and%20Macbeth's%20soliloquy%20%26quot%3BLife's%20but%20a%20walking%20shadow%26quot%3B%2C%20Scribe's%20I%20Love%20You%2C%20Pav%20Bhaji%20and%20Nina%20Simone's%20%26quot%3BSinnerman%26quot%3B%20and%20AR%20Rahman's%20Tu%20hi%20re%20tere%20bina%20main%20kaise%20jiyu%20(from%20Mani%20Ratnam's%20Bombay)%20and%20you%20have%20one%20of%20the%20most%20aurally%20varied%20Indian%20web%20shows%20ever.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20tangible%20physical%20dimensions%20of%20the%20quaint%20world%20that%20Anuj%20Rakesh%20Dhawan's%20camera%20captures%20add%20to%20the%20allure.%20Roads%20snake%20around%20verdant%20valleys.%20Undulating%20hills%20strain%20to%20pierce%20the%20clouds.%20But%20under%20the%20town's%20sleepy%20surface%2C%20forbidden%20desire%2C%20thwarted%20ambition%2C%20blackmail%20and%20unholy%20collusions%20form%20a%20deadly%20broth.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20she%20runs%20out%20patience%20and%20options%2C%20Swathi%20resorts%20to%20desperate%20measures.%20Umesh%20is%20dragged%20along%2C%20sometimes%20kicking%20and%20whining%2C%20at%20others%20dithering%20but%20giving%20in.%20With%20their%20lives%2C%20relationships%20and%20businesses%20are%20a%20%26quot%3Bbloody%26quot%3B%20mess.%20The%20men%20and%20women%20in%20Killer%20Soup%20are%20like%20trotters%20in%20a%20soup.%20The%20more%20they%20try%20to%20wriggle%20out%2C%20the%20worse%20it%20gets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESwathi%20isn't%20the%20only%20woman%20striving%20for%20a%20room%20of%20her%20own%20in%20%3Cem%3EKiller%20Soup%3C%2Fem%3E.%20Arvind's%20only%20daughter%2C%20Apeksha%20'Appu'%20Shetty%20(Anula%20Navlekar)%2C%20aspires%20to%20be%20an%20artist.%20She%20earns%20a%20call-up%20from%20a%20prestigious%20Paris%20art%20school.%20But%20her%20father%20ridicules%20her%20for%20the%20nudes%20she%20draws.%20He%20insists%20she'd%20be%20better%20off%20taking%20charge%20of%20the%20family%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKirtima%20(Kani%20Kusruti)%2C%20an%20accountant%20in%20Prabhu's%20firm%20and%20a%20Kalari%20exponent%2C%20has%20ambitions%20beyond%20the%20custard%20tarts%20she%20makes%20to%20show%20up%20Swathi's%20paya%20soup%2C%20which%20lacks%20a%20secret%20ingredient%20that%20khansama%20Mehrunisa%20(Vaishali%20Bisht%20in%20a%20cameo%20of%20substance)%20is%20loath%20to%20part%20with.%20Could%20there%20be%20more%20to%20the%20rivalry%20between%20Swathi%20and%20Kirtima%3F%20Nothing%20that%20is%20on%20the%20oven%20in%C2%A0%3Cem%3EKiller%20Soup%3C%2Fem%3E%20is%20to%20be%20discounted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EKiller%20Soup%3C%2Fem%3E%20is%20a%20police%20procedural%2C%20too.%20Inspector%20Hassan%20(Nassar)%2C%20weeks%20away%20from%20retirement%2C%20is%20in%20no%20hurry%20to%20get%20to%20the%20bottom%20of%20Swathi's%20claim%20that%20her%20husband%20was%20attacked%20with%20acid.%20He%20isn't%20exactly%20a%20bumbling%20cop%20nor%20is%20he%20a%20cynical%20pro.%20As%20he%20says%20to%20a%20junior%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20don't%20get%20paid%20to%20think.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20Thupalli%20(Anbuthasan)%2C%20a%20rookie%20cop%2C%20is%20one%20determined%20bloke.%20Mixing%20poetry%20with%20policing%2C%20he%20is%20at%20the%20centre%20of%20several%20surreal%20encounters%20with%20Inspector%20Hassan%20as%20the%20latter%20looks%20for%20clues%20in%20hidden%20in%20verse.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChaubey%20makes%20his%20first%20web%20show%20count%20well%20beyond%20the%20mere%20generic.%20The%20terrain%20he%20explores%20in%20%3Cem%3EKiller%20Soup%3C%2Fem%3E%20is%20far%20removed%20from%20the%20dusty%20upcountry%20locations%20of%20%3Cem%3EIshqiya%20%3C%2Fem%3Eand%20%3Cem%3ESonchiriya%3C%2Fem%3E.%20The%20geographical%20shift%20yields%20a%20captivating%20show%20that%20alternates%20between%20slow-burn%20and%20breakneck%20without%20the%20slightest%20wobble%20in%20its%20tonal%20consistency.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EKiller%20Soup%3C%2Fem%3E%20abides%20steadfastly%20by%20its%20neo-noir%20principles%20but%20the%20flawed%20characters%20that%20populate%20the%20narrative%20aren't%20evil%20in%20the%20conventional%20sense.%20They%20are%20at%20worst%20crooked%20and%20self-serving.%20Significantly%2C%20none%20of%20the%20killings%20that%20occur%2C%20nor%20their%20aftermath%2C%20is%20premeditated.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBajpayee%20and%20Sen%20Sharma%20take%20on%20roles%20unlike%20any%20other%20that%20they%20have%20played%20before.%20They%20strike%20up%20a%20wonderful%20duet%2C%20challenging%20and%20enhancing%20each%20other%20in%20a%20cat-and-mouse%20game%20in%20which%20predator%20and%20victim%20frequently%20swap%20places%20and%20co-conspirators%20often%20work%20at%20cross-purposes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%20Nassar%20as%20the%20avuncular%20inspector%2C%20Lal%2C%20cast%20Appu's%20maternal%20uncle%20and%20an%20Arvind%20Shetty%20aide%20who%20pulls%20his%20punches%2C%20and%20Sayaji%20Shinde%20steal%20many%20a%20scene.%20Kani%20Kusruti%20delivers%20an%20exceptionally%20effortless%20performance.%20No%20less%20noteworthy%20is%20Anula%20Navlekar%20as%20a%20woman%20trapped%20in%20a%20hellhole.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20background%20score%20by%20Benedict%20Taylor%20and%20Naren%20Chandavarkar%20is%20a%20delectable%20smorgasbord%20of%20sounds.%20They%20flow%20through%20the%20show%20like%20rippling%20water%20down%20a%20stream%20that%20constantly%20changes%20its%20pace%20and%20rhythm%20in%20sync%20with%20the%20winds%20and%20the%20rains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESen%20Sharma's%20character%20asks%20as%20the%20show%20winds%20down%3A%20%26quot%3BKaisa%20laga%20sabko%20mera%20soup%20(how%20did%20you%20all%20like%20my%20soup)%3F%26quot%3B%20The%20unequivocal%20answer%3A%20We%20love%20it.%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704963480000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2F4t2t7j_gg_625x300_11_January_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Fkiller-soup-review-konkona-sen-sharma-manoj-bajpayee-strike-a-wonderful-duet-in-deadly-b