0TMC%20leaders.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fother-states%2Fmagnitude-of-the-10000-crore-pds-scam-in-west-bengal-is-enormous-ed%2Farticle67720001.ece%5C%22%3EED%20submissions%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Adhya%20played%20a%20direct%20role%20in%20laundering%20approximately%20Rs%2010%2C000%20crores%20through%20foreign%20currency%20trading%20and%20exchange%20in%20the%20border%20areas%20of%20the%20state%2C%20with%20nearly%20half%20of%20that%20sum%20stemming%20from%20the%20ration%20distribution%20scam.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20The%20agency%20claimed%20in%20court%20that%20Adhya%20managed%20to%20smuggle%20out%20over%20Rs%202%2C500%20crores%20to%20Dubai%20through%20forex%20trade.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fkolkata%2Fday-after-attack-on-ed-officials-hunt-begins-for-tmc-leader-sheikh-shahjahan%2Farticleshow%2F106603062.cms%5C%22%3ESheikh%20Shahjahan%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20other%20key%20suspect%2C%20remains%20at%20large%20despite%20an%20ED%20look-out%20circular%20(LOC)%20issued%20for%20him.%20The%20LOC%20was%20issued%20after%20an%20armed%20mob%20attacked%20investigating%20agencies%20during%20a%20raid%20in%20Sandeshkhali%2C%20North%2024%20Parganas%2C%20last%20Friday%20(January%205).%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EWhat%20is%20the%20ration%20scam%20in%20West%20Bengal%3F%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDuring%20the%20COVID-19%20lockdown%20in%20May%202020%2C%20protests%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fcities%2Fkolkata%2Faccused-of-irregularities-in-pds-ration-dealers-house-ransacked-in-murshidabad-6391017%2F%5C%22%3Eerupted%20in%20West%20Bengal%3C%2Fa%3E%20over%20alleged%20irregularities%20in%20the%20distribution%20of%20PDS%20grains.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20first%20information%20report%20(FIR)%20was%20filed%20in%20Nadia%20district.%20Then-governor%20of%20West%20Bengal%20Jagdeep%20Dhankhar%20(now%20vice%20president)%2C%20and%20the%20central%20government%20had%20criticised%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20handling%20of%20the%20PDS.%20On%20April%2023%2C%202020%2C%20the%20Centre%20informed%20the%20state%20that%20food%20grain%20distribution%20was%20non-existent%20under%20the%20Pradhan%20Mantri%20Garib%20Kalyan%20Anna%20Yojana%20(PMGKAY).%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fin-bengals-sandeshkhali-controversial-tmc-leader-sheikh-shahjahans-hold-is-powerful%5C%22%3E%20In%20Bengal%E2%80%99s%20Sandeshkhali%2C%20Controversial%20TMC%20Leader%20Sheikh%20Shahjahan%E2%80%99s%20Hold%20Is%20Powerful%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fexplained%2Fed-crpf-attacked-west-bengal-pds-scam-9098098%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EIndian%20Express%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20under%20PMGKAY%2C%20each%20ration%20card%20holder%20was%20entitled%20to%205%20kilogram%20of%20food%20grains%20and%201%20kg%20of%20pulses%2C%20in%20addition%20to%20the%20monthly%20quota%20of%205%20kg%20of%20subsidised%20food%20grains%20per%20person%20under%20the%20National%20Food%20Security%20Act%20(NFSA).%20Investigations%20revealed%20that%20an%20influential%20businessman%2C%20Bakibur%20Rahman%2C%20supplied%20rice%20and%20wheat%20in%20insufficient%20quantities%20to%20fair%20price%20shop%20distributors.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBakibur%2C%20allegedly%20supported%20by%20Mallick%2C%20a%20powerful%20minister%20close%20to%20the%20chief%20minister%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eprofited%20by%20selling%20the%20excess%20grain%20in%20the%20open%20market.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EED%20sources%20claim%20that%20flour%20mill%20owners%20supplied%20less%20flour%20to%20distributors%20than%20paid%20for%20by%20the%20government.%20Mill%20owners%20claimed%20that%20for%20the%20price%20of%201%20kg%20of%20flour%2C%20government%20suppliers%20received%20only%20about%20600%20grams.%20Approximately%2030%25%20of%20the%20PDS%20ration%20intended%20for%20beneficiaries%20in%20West%20Bengal%20was%20redirected%20to%20the%20open%20market.%20In%20collaboration%20with%20some%20local%20leaders%20from%20the%20ruling%20party%2C%20rice%20millers%20created%20fake%20bank%20accounts%20for%20farmers%2C%20siphoning%20off%20the%20minimum%20support%20price%20(MSP)%20earmarked%20for%20paddy%20growers.%20Rice%20millers%20earned%20nearly%20Rs%20200%20per%20quintal%20for%20grains%20that%20government%20agencies%20were%20supposed%20to%20procure%20at%20MSP%20from%20farmers%2C%20of%20which%2C%20a%20significant%20percentage%20had%20allegedly%20to%20be%20shared%20with%20Mallick%2C%20who%20oversaw%20the%20Food%20and%20Supplies%20Ministry%20in%20the%20previous%20TMC%20government%20from%202016%20to%202021.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fpartha-chatterjee-ssc-scam-tmc-manata-corruption%5C%22%3EPartha%20Chatterjee%2C%20another%20major%20leader%20currently%20in%20jail%2C%20had%20to%20lose%20his%20portfolio%3C%2Fa%3E%20after%20his%20involvement%20in%20the%20job%20recruitment%20scam%20came%20to%20light%2C%20Mallick%20continues%20to%20remain%20a%20minister%20holding%20key%20position%20in%20the%20cabinet.%20Similarly%2C%20Shahjahan%20and%20Adhya%2C%20crucial%20figures%20in%20TMC%E2%80%99s%20electoral%20strategy%20in%20North%2024%20Parganas%2C%20continue%20to%20enjoy%20party%20support%20despite%20being%20confronted%20with%20accusations%20spanning%20from%20financial%20misconduct%20to%20homicide.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERecently%2C%20Shovandev%20Chattopadhyay%2C%20a%20seasoned%20TMC%20leader%2C%20cautioned%20that%20ED%20officials%20can%20anticipate%20similar%20resistance%20from%20TMC%20student%20activists%20in%20the%20days%20ahead%2C%20leading%20to%20public%20outcry.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDuring%20the%20panchayat%20elections%20in%202013%2C%202018%2C%20and%202023%2C%20opposition%20parties%20struggled%20to%20field%20candidates%20in%20the%20Sadeshkhali%20blocks%2C%20where%20Shahjahan%20wields%20significant%20political%20influence.%20Likewise%2C%20Adhya%E2%80%99s%20influence%20in%20the%20Matua-dominated%20border%20areas%20near%20Bangaon%20became%20evident%20when%20ED%20officials%20encountered%20resistance%20from%20his%20supporters.%20Following%20his%20arrest%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Emany%20locals%20came%20forward%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fer-tmc-councillor-said-in-bangaon-985709.html%5C%22%3Edisclosed%3C%2Fa%3E%20his%20involvement%20in%20corruption%2C%20intimidation%2C%20and%20violence%20to%20the%20local%20media%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20corruption%20in%20ration%20distribution%20poses%20a%20threat%20to%20the%20TMC%20organisation%20as%20there%20are%20tens%20of%20Shahjahan%20within%20the%20party.%20Their%20potential%20arrests%20could%20exert%20pressure%20on%20the%20party%2C%20leading%20to%20a%20cascading%20effect%20on%20its%20influence%2C%E2%80%9D%20observed%20political%20analyst%20Biswanath%20Chakraborty.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fpartha-chatterjee-ssc-scam-tmc-manata-corruption%5C%22%3ETMC%20May%20Have%20Sacked%20Partha%20Chatterjee%2C%20But%20Its%20Problems%20With%20Corruption%20Run%20Deep%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20part%20of%20the%20collusion%2C%20ration%20dealers%20were%20compelled%20to%20contribute%20a%20portion%20of%20their%20monthly%20earnings%20to%20the%20local%20syndicate%20in%20exchange%20for%20the%20windfall.%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20spoke%20to%20a%20ration%20dealer%20in%20Murshidabad%2C%20whose%20identity%20is%20being%20withheld%20for%20protection.%20The%20dealer%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20amount%20of%20money%20we%E2%80%99re%20paying%20as%20bribe%20and%20commission%20to%20the%20local%20syndicate%20kept%20on%20increasing.%20Many%20of%20us%20felt%20the%20dealership%20was%20not%20profitable%20anymore.%20I%20applied%20three%20years%20back%20to%20return%20my%20licence%2C%20but%20it%20was%20not%20accepted.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20a%20family%20of%20five%2C%20each%20with%20ration%20cards.%20Yet%2C%20we%20receive%20only%2012%20kgs%20of%20rice%20every%20month%20from%20the%20ration%20shop.%20I%20use%20ration%20cards%20from%20other%20families%20who%20do%20not%20want%20to%20eat%20this%20rice%2C%20but%20are%20eligible%20for%20rations.%20I%20pay%20them%20Rs%2025%20per%20kg%20for%20their%20share%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Tapan%20Roy%2C%20a%20part-time%20transport%20worker%20from%20Dhupguri%20in%20North%20Bengal.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%202007%2C%20during%20the%20tenure%20of%20the%20Buddhadeb%20Bhattacharjee-led%20Left%20Front%20government%2C%20protests%20erupted%20over%20alleged%20irregularities%20in%20the%20public%20distribution%20system.%20One%20of%20the%20demonstrations%2C%20marked%20by%20violence%2C%20resulted%20in%20the%20death%20of%20Ayub%20Sheikh%2C%20a%20protester%2C%20in%20a%20clash%20with%20the%20police.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20recently%20visited%20Ayub%E2%80%99s%20family%2C%20who%20now%20claim%20to%20have%20received%20insufficient%20rations.%20Jhunafa%20Bibi%2C%20Ayub%E2%80%99s%20wife%2C%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CSometimes%20the%20rice%20arrives%20in%20a%20month%2C%20sometimes%20it%20doesn%E2%80%99t.%20Kerosene%20is%20unavailable.%20Previously%2C%20lentils%20were%20accessible%3B%20now%20there%20are%20none.%20Wheat%20flour%20arrives%20irregularly%2C%20and%20the%20quality%20is%20very%20poor!%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ETranslated%20from%20Bangla%20to%20English%20by%20Aparna%20Bhattacharya.%3C%