o%20I%20loved%20because%20he%20had%20a%20huge%20photograph%20of%20my%20Guru%20Begum%20Akhtar%20at%20the%20very%20entrance%20of%20his%20home%3B%20his%20wife%20Malavika%20Kanan%2C%20who%20said%20she%20never%20read%20any%20newspaper%20in%20the%20morning%20because%20all%20the%20bad%20news%20ruined%20her%20day%3B%20the%20stern-faced%20Ustad%20Nisar%20Hussain%20Khan%2C%20Rashid%E2%80%99s%20mentor%20and%20guru%2C%20a%20man%20of%20few%20words%20and%20an%20uncompromising%20demeanour%3B%20Pandit%20Jagdish%20Prasad%20whose%20wife%20would%20complain%20unabashedly%20that%20he%20kept%20her%20awake%20all%20night%3B%20Pandit%20Sunil%20Bose%20and%20Pandit%20Ajoy%20Chakraborty%20who%20was%20then%20a%20scholar-musician.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVijay%20Kichlu%20was%20at%20the%20helm%20of%20affairs%20as%20the%20director%20of%20SRA.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20jointly%20mentored%20and%20assessed%20each%20%E2%80%98scholar%E2%80%99%20once%20a%20week.%20About%20Rashid%2C%20they%20would%20say%20amongst%20themselves%2C%20%E2%80%9CWho%20are%20we%20to%20assess%20him%3F%20He%E2%80%99s%20our%20equal%2C%20not%20less%20than%20us%E2%80%9D.%20They%20too%20were%20in%20awe%20of%20his%20brilliance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20used%20to%20come%20over%20in%20the%20evenings%20to%20Girija%20Devi%20or%20%3Cem%3EAppa%20ji%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%98s%20house%20often%2C%20and%20would%20regale%20us%20with%20his%20mimicry.%20He%20used%20to%20do%20a%20hilarious%20Bharatnatyam%20%3Cem%3Ebhav-dikhana%3C%2Fem%3E%20act%20of%20a%20famous%20dancer%20and%20would%20have%20us%20all%20in%20splits.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20he%20had%20fallen%20madly%20in%20love%20with%20the%20woman%20who%20he%20eventually%20married%2C%20and%20was%20tortured%20by%20his%20guru%20%E2%80%98s%20command%20to%20marry%20his%20relative%20instead.%20At%20that%20time%2C%20I%20was%20his%20confidant.%20He%20would%20speak%20to%20me%20of%20his%20despair%20and%20complained%20bitterly%20that%20his%20guru%20would%20order%20him%20to%20run%20errands%20all%20morning%20when%20he%20wanted%20to%20do%20practice%20music%20instead.%20We%20shared%20grouses%20against%20our%20gurus%20and%20felt%20we%20were%20at%20their%20mercy.%20I%20found%20my%20guru%20unkind%20as%20I%20constantly%20compared%20her%20with%20my%20first%20guru%2C%20Begum%20Akhtar%2C%20who%20was%20extremely%20indulgent.%20Later%2C%20I%20loved%20Girija%20Devi%20too%2C%20as%20I%20am%20sure%20Rashid%20also%20came%20to%20love%20his%20guru.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERashid%20and%20I%20met%20backstage%20before%20one%20of%20his%20concerts%20some%20years%20later%20and%20he%20chided%20me%3A%20%E2%80%9CLook%20where%20I%20have%20reached%E2%80%A6why%20aren%E2%80%99t%20you%20better%20known%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20music%20shone%20through%20his%20profound%20honesty%2C%20which%20was%20reflected%20in%20his%20gaze%20towards%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EHere%20are%20four%20renditions%20by%20Rashid%20Khan%20chosen%20by%20Rekha%20Surya%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fshare%2Fr%2FpJMRHRid9G2b61RY%2F%3Fmibextid%3Dqi2Omg%5C%22%3E1%3C%2Fa%3E%20%7C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fshare%2Fr%2FDPsz6ALK8dLBecVC%2F%3Fmibextid%3Dqi2Omg%5C%22%3E2%3C%2Fa%3E%20%7C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fshare%2Fr%2F1Wihd34o1zkFraTe%2F%3Fmibextid%3Dqi2Omg%5C%22%3E3%3C%2Fa%3E%20%7C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fshare%2Fr%2FCQUpNMsRHbwsi45z%2F%3Fmibextid%3Dqi2Omg%5C%22%3E4%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EHindustani%20semi-classical%20singer%20Rekha%20Surya%20is%20the%20youngest%20disciple%20of%20Begum%20Akhtar%20and%20later%20trained%20under%20Girija%20Devi.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704961852000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F11130712%2FUntitled-design-9-1.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fthe-arts%2Fclassical-musician-rashid-khan-obituary%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20warm%20tribute%20to%2