ts%20seen%20as%20referring%20to%20Pakistan's%20continuing%20support%20for%20cross-border%20terrorism.%20General%20Pande%2C%20addressing%20the%20Army's%20annual%20press%20conference%2C%20called%20the%20situation%20in%20those%20two%20regions%20a%20%26quot%3Bsource%20of%20concern%26quot%3B%2C%20and%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThere%20was%20peace%20there%20till%202017%2F18%20(but)%20this%20is%20now%20an%20area%20where%20our%20adversaries%20have%20been%20active...%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20the%20last%20five%20to%20six%20months%2C%20in%20Rajouri%20and%20Poonch%2C%20there%20has%20been%20increase%20in%20terrorism.%20This%20is%20a%20matter%20of%20concern.%20If%20you%20see...%20before%202003%20terrorism%20in%20that%20area%20was%20eradicated%2C%20and%20peace%20was%20there%20till%202017%2F18.%20But%20now%2C%20because%20of%20the%20situation%20normalising%20in%20the%20Valley%2C%20our%20adversaries%20are%20active%20there.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20terms%20of%20abetting%20terrorism%20and%20encouraging%20proxy%20tanzeems%20(proxies%20of%20known%20terror%20groups)...%20In%20the%20last%20three%20years%2045%20terrorists%20were%20eliminated%20in%20this%20area.%20Last%20year%20alone%20there%20were%20five%20infiltration%20bids%2C%20which%20were%20foiled%2C%20and%20six%20terrorists%20were%20eliminated%20in%20those%20attempts.%20Even%20in%20the%20hinterland%20about%2014%20terrorists%20were%20neutralised%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20General%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FWATCH%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23WATCH%3C%2Fa%3E%20%7C%20Delhi%3A%20COAS%20General%20Manoj%20Pande%20says%2C%20%26quot%3B...The%20situation%20and%20terrorist%20activities%20in%20Rajouri%20and%20Poonch%20in%20the%20last%205-6%20months%20have%20been%20an%20issue%20of%20concern%20to%20us.%20By%202003%2C%20terrorism%20in%20this%20area%20was%20fully%20disseminated%20and%20peace%20was%20established%20there%20till%202017-18.%20Because%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2F51qKjri54p%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2F51qKjri54p%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20ANI%20(%40ANI)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FANI%2Fstatus%2F1745341620927762608%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJanuary%2011%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3EGeneral%20Pande%20also%20shared%20a%20nine-point%20action%20plan%20to%20improve%20the%20situation%20in%20Rajouri%2C%20including%20enhanced%20intelligence%20gathering%20and%20better%20synergy%20with%20police%20and%20local%20security%20officials.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20nine%20points%20outlined%20by%20the%20General%20also%20include%20an%20emphasis%20on%20outreach%20to%20local%20populations%20and%20respect%20for%20human%20rights%2C%20both%20of%20which%20are%20crucial%20messages%20in%20the%20light%20of%20the%20death%20of%20three%20civilians%20after%20they%20were%20detained%20for%20questioning%20following%20a%20terror%20attack%20in%20Poonch%20that%20killed%20four%20soldiers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEnhanced%20deployment%20and%20reorienting%20specific%20units%2C%20as%20well%20as%20human%20intelligence%2C%20and%20use%20of%20technology%20and%20instituting%20learnings%20from%20previous%20encounters%20are%20also%20key%2C%20the%20General%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Army%20Chief's%20comments%20come%20after%20multiple%20terror%20attacks%20in%20the%20Poonch%20and%20Rajouri%20areas%2C%20including%20an%20ambush%20of%20two%20military%20vehicles%20in%20the%20former%20district%20last%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Farmy-truck-ambushed-by-terrorists-in-jammu-and-kashmirs-poonch-district-4716346%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFour%20Soldiers%20Killed%20In%20Encounter%20With%20Terrorists%20In%20J%26amp%3BK's%20Poonch%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3