s%20and%20strove%20with%20hope%20to%20build%20a%20%E2%80%9CSovereign%20Socialist%20Secular%20Democratic%20Republic%20committed%20to%20Justice%2C%20Equality%20and%20Liberty%20for%20the%20people.%E2%80%9D%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20respecting%20and%20treating%20the%20panoply%20of%20religions%20without%20fear%20or%20favour%2C%20the%20framers%20of%20our%20constitution%20clearly%20did%20not%20intend%20for%20the%20state%20to%20involve%20itself%20in%20promoting%20any%20form%20of%20religion.%20Instead%2C%20they%20advocated%20a%20secular%20humanism%20that%20propagated%20a%20separation%20of%20religious%20activities%20and%20state%20functions.%20It%20has%20been%20a%20rocky%20journey%20with%20many%20misses%20and%20some%20hits%2C%20but%20today%2C%20the%20noble%20aspirations%20expressed%20in%20the%20preamble%20to%20the%20constitution%20seem%20like%20an%20absurd%20fantasy%2C%20a%20cruel%20joke.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20is%20no%20longer%20the%20country%20that%20our%20founding%20fathers%20fought%20and%20died%20for.%20The%20cosmopolitan%20spirit%20of%20brotherhood%2C%20tolerance%20and%20inclusion%20has%20been%20all%20but%20snuffed%20out%20by%20the%20creeping%20majoritarianism%20and%20perverse%20hyper-nationalism%20sweeping%20across%20the%20land.%20Religion%20is%20now%20deployed%20as%20a%20dubious%20expedient%20for%20gaining%20worldly%20control.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20remember%20Arun%20Shourie%2C%20arguably%20the%20most%20intrepid%20editor%20in%20former%20Prime%20Minister%20Indira%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20time%2C%20lambasting%20her%20conduct%20during%20her%20election%20campaign%20in%20Chikmagalur%20in%201978%2C%20pointing%20out%20her%20hypocrisy%20in%20%E2%80%9Cpreaching%20secularism%20in%20between%20visits%20to%20every%20temple%20in%20the%20vicinity.%E2%80%9D%20Religiosity%20in%20the%20public%20square%20was%20then%20frowned%20upon.%20Today%2C%20religion%20has%20not%20only%20become%20integral%20to%20politics%2C%20but%20the%20flaunting%20of%20religious%20fervour%20has%20become%20%3Cem%3Ede%20rigueur%3C%2Fem%3E%20for%20any%20politician%20who%20wants%20to%20%E2%80%98make%20it%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F08%2F07083139%2F2020_8img05_Aug_2020_PTI05-08-2020_000172B.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F08%2F07083139%2F2020_8img05_Aug_2020_PTI05-08-2020_000172B.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F08%2F07083139%2F2020_8img05_Aug_2020_PTI05-08-2020_000172B-300x190.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F08%2F07083139%2F2020_8img05_Aug_2020_PTI05-08-2020_000172B-1024x649.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-471716%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22761%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EPM%20Narendra%20Modi%20takes%20part%20in%20the%20bhoomi%20pujan%20for%20the%20construction%20of%20a%20Ram%20temple%20in%20Ayodhya%2C%20August%205%2C%202020.%20Photo%3A%20PIB%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETo%20reductively%20brush%20off%20the%20buzz%20around%20the%20January%2022%20Ram%20Mandir%20inauguration%20as%20a%20gimmick%20for%20electoral%20purposes%20would%20be%20a%20complete%20misreading%20of%20a%20grim%20situation.%20The%20planned%20mass%20mobilisation%20of%20the%20majority%20community%20%E2%80%93%20the%20running%20of%201%2C000%20trains%20to%20Ayodhya%20from%20various%20parts%20of%20the%20country%2C%20the%20ruling%20party%E2%80%99s%20arrangements%20to%20host%2050%2C000%20pilgrims%20every%20day%2C%20the%20invitation%20to%20150%20disparate%20groups%20cutting%20across%20caste%20lines%C2%A0%20and%204%2C000%C2%A0%20holy%20men%20for%20the%20consecration%20ceremony%2C%20the%20installation%20of%205%20lakh%20LED%20screens%20in%20temples%2C%20the%20prime%20minster%E2%80%99s%20injunction%20to%20celebrate%20January%2022%20as%20Diwali%20by%20lighting%20diyas%20at%20home%20%E2%80%93%20is%20nothing%20less%20than%20a%20carefully%20calibrated%20campaign%20of%20consolidation%20of%20Hindu%20society%20and%20a%20call%20to%20arms%20for%20furthering%20the%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3Ekamandal%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D%20project%20whose%20ultimate%20mission%20is%20the%20reclaiming%20of%20temples%2C%20implementation%20of%20the%20uniform%20civil%20code%2C%20ban%20on%20cow%20slaughter%2C%20halal%20meat%2C%20the%20hijab%20and%20a%20lot%20more.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20clear%20subterranean%20text%20is%20not%20difficult%20to%20guess%2C%20which%20is%20the%20%E2%80%9Cothering%E2%80%9D%20of%20minorities%20and%20Muslims%20in%20particular.%20At%20its%20core%2C%20the%20mobilisation%20of%20the%20masses%20(only%20Hindu)%20for%20the%20Ram%20temple%20consecration%20is%20clearly%20intended%20to%20whip%20up%20a%20communal%20consensus%20on%20a%20Hindu%20Rashtra.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Freligion%2Fsanatan-hindu-dharma-highest-guru-ram-temple%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Why%204%20Highest%20Gurus%20of%20Sanatan%20Hindu%20Dharma%20Won%E2%80%99t%20Participate%20in%20Ram%20Temple%20Pranpratistha%2C%E2%80%99%20Explains%20Pro-Hindutva%20Portal%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20are%20disturbing%20markers%20that%20capture%20the%20zeitgeist%20of%20our%20times%20%E2%80%93%20of%20a%20majoritarian%20State%20that%20is%20on%20a%20mission%20to%20reduce%20the%20minorities%20to%20second-class%20citizens.%20The%20Ram%20temple%20is%20not%20quite%20done%20but%20there%20are%20already%20menacing%20rumblings%20around%20the%20Gyanvapi%20masjid%20in%20Varanasi%20and%20the%20Shahi%20Idgah%20mosque%20in%20Mathura.%20We%20know%20by%20now%20that%20the%20slogan%2C%20%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EYeh%20to%20sirf%20jhanki%20hai%2C%20Kashi-Mathura%20baaki%20hai%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E(This%20is%20just%20a%20trailer%2C%20Kashi%20and%20Mathura%20are%20still%20pending)%E2%80%9D%2C%20is%20no%20idle%20boast!%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOur%20home%20minister%2C%20who%20says%20it%20like%20it%20is%2C%20has%20announced%20to%20the%20world%20that%20the%20Citizens%20Amendment%20Act%20(CAA)%2C%20which%20brazenly%20discriminates%20against%20Muslims%2C%20will%20soon%20be%20implemented.%20As%20ominous%20is%20his%20calculated%20statement%20that%20Modi%20had%20cured%20Gujarat%20of%20riots%20by%20teaching%20rioters%20(read%20Muslims)%20a%20lesson%20in%202002.%20By%20obliquely%20suggesting%20that%20Modi%20had%20presided%20over%20the%20nightmarish%20events%20in%20the%20aftermath%20of%20the%20Godhra%20train%20burning%2C%20the%20home%20minister%20is%20thumbing%20a%20nose%20at%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20verdict%20exonerating%20Modi%20of%20any%20involvement%20in%20the%20genocide%20that%20followed%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20Godhra.%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20closest%20aide%20has%20made%20this%20provocative%20claim%20because%20he%20knows%20that%20for%20millions%20of%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20followers%2C%20the%20undying%20faith%20in%20Modi%20stems%20primarily%20from%20their%20fond%20belief%20that%20he%20is%20the%20only%20leader%20who%20can%20deal%20effectively%20with%20the%20%E2%80%9CMuslim%20menace.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOf%20a%20piece%20with%20the%20planned%2C%20all-out%20offensive%20against%20Muslims%20is%20the%20obnoxious%2C%20dastardly%20attack%20on%20the%20Muslim%20community%20by%20BJP%20MP%20Ramesh%20Bidhuri%20from%20within%20the%20sacred%20precincts%20of%20Parliament%20even%20as%20senior%20BJP%20members%20beamed%20with%20delight.%20No%20action%20was%20taken%20against%20him.%20In%20a%20hate-filled%20environment%20that%20thrives%20on%20Muslim%20bashing%2C%20this%20hate-monger%20could%20well%20be%20the%20new%20poster%20boy%20of%20the%20BJP%20like%20Yogi%20Adityanath%20and%20Sadhvi%20Pragya%20before%20him.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Freligion%2Fsanatan-strikes-back-how-dare-modi-perform-the-consecration-ceremony-asks-a-priest%5C%22%3ESanatan%20Strikes%20Back%3A%20%E2%80%98How%20Dare%20Modi%20Perform%20the%20Consecration%20Ceremony%2C%E2%80%99%20Asks%20a%20Priest%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20present%20regime%20has%20smashed%20the%20flimsy%20secular%20facade%20that%20corralled%20the%20state%20from%20religion%2C%20which%20is%20now%20front%20and%20centre%20in%20the%20public%20arena%20and%20the%20ultimate%20arbiter%20of%20temporal%20power.%20The%20savage%20conduct%20of%20the%20%3Cem%3Etrishul%3C%2Fem%3E-brandishing%20%3Cem%3Ebhakts%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%20recent%20years%20under%20the%20benign%20gaze%20of%20the%20state%2C%20vindicates%20Italian%20philosopher%20Umberto%20Eco%E2%80%99s%20observation%20that%20ordinary%20people%20are%20never%20so%20completely%20and%20enthusiastically%20evil%20as%20when%20they%20act%20out%20of%20religious%20conviction.%20The%20collective%20delirium%20over%20the%20consecration%20of%20the%20Ram%20temple%20at%20Ayodhya%20under%20the%20aegis%20of%20the%20Modi%20government%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0represents%20the%20emphatic%20triumph%20of%20religious%20fundamentalism%20over%20secularism%2C%20of%20Hindutva%20over%20Hinduism%2C%20of%20religiosity%20over%20religion%2C%20of%20exclusion%20over%20inclusion%2C%20of%20hate%20over%20brotherhood.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERam%20must%20be%20distraught%2C%20if%20not%20enraged%2C%20at%20what%20is%20being%20done%20in%20his%20name.%20He%20is%20the%20epitome%20of%20justice%2C%20compassion%2C%20peace%20and%20non-violence.%20He%20personifies%20truthfulness%2C%20forgiveness%2C%20accountability%20and%20empathy%20with%20his%20subjects.%20From%20the%20%3Cem%3ERamayana%3C%2Fem%3E%20we%20know%20that%20Ram%20was%20the%20perfect%20son%2C%20the%20ideal%20husband%20and%20the%20quintessentially%20responsible%20ruler.%20As%20depicted%20in%20the%20%3Cem%3ERamayana%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Ram%E2%80%99s%20story%20in%20essence%20embodies%20the%20victory%20of%20righteousness%20over%20evil%20and%20the%20advent%20of%20Ram%20Rajya.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20greatest%20Indian%20and%20Hindu%2C%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%20who%20was%20deeply%20influenced%20by%20the%20%3Cem%3ERamayana%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20in%20an%20expository%20piece%20that%20appeared%20in%20%3Cem%3EYoung%20Indian%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%201929%2C%20explained%20what%20Ram%20Rajya%20means%3A%20%E2%80%9CBy%20Ram%20Rajya%2C%20I%20do%20not%20mean%20Hindu%20Raj.%20I%20mean%20Ram%20Raj%2C%20the%20kingdom%20of%20God.%20For%20me%20Ram%20and%20Rahim%20are%20one%20and%20the%20same%3B%20I%20acknowledge%20no%20other%20God%20but%20the%20one%20God%20of%20truth%20and%20righteousness.%E2%80%9D%20For%20the%20Mahatma%2C%20Ram%20Rajya%20meant%20equal%20citizenship%20%E2%80%93%20%E2%80%9Cequal%20rights%20to%20both%20prince%20and%20pauper.%E2%80%9D%20Is%20it%20any%20surprise%20then%20that%20Gandhism%20is%20viewed%20as%20a%20mortal%20enemy%20of%20Hindutva%3F%20But%20by%20the%20looks%20of%20it%2C%20Hindutva%20is%20up%20and%20running%20and%20to%20hell%20with%20Gandhiji%20and%20secularism.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20grand%20consecration%20on%20January%2022%20is%20slated%20to%20be%20the%20greatest%20politico-religious%20event%20of%20our%20time%20and%20will%20be%20presided%20over%20by%20the%20high%20priest%20of%20Hindutva%2C%20the%20prime%20minister%20himself.%20But%20far%20from%20being%20the%20crowning%20glory%20of%20a%20great%20religion%2C%20the%20Ram%20Mandir%2C%20built%20on%20the%20ruins%20of%20a%20mosque%20vandalised%20by%20religious%20fanatics%20and%20now%20in%20the%20hands%20of%20the%20vandals%20and%20their%20mentors%20is%2C%20in%20truth%2C%20a%20symbol%20of%20the%20triumph%20of%20majoritarian%20nationalism.%20As%20an%20outlier%20who%20has%20watched%20with%20cold%20fear%20the%20march%20of%20Hindutva%20to%20the%20centre%20of%20our%20national%20life%2C%20the%20Ram%20temple%20symbolises%20the%20formal%20investiture%20of%20the%20Hindu%20Rashtra%20and%20the%20death%20of%20secular%20India.%20One%20wonders%20what%20our%20founding%20fathers%20would%20have%20thought%20of%20such%20a%20radical%20transmutation%20of%20the%20body%20politic.%C2%A0%20Their%20angst%20can%20best%20be%20expressed%20by%20invoking%20Mahatma%E2%80%99s%20last%20anguished%20cry%3A%20%E2%80%9CHey%20Ram!%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EMathew%20John%20is%20a%20former%20civil%20servant.%20The%20views%20are%20personal.%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704957345000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F11121926%2FScreenshot-2024-01-11-at-12.18.29-PM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fdelirium-over-ram-mandir-a-nation-consecrated-or-desecrated%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20collective%20hullaballoo%20over%20the%20consecration%20of%20the%20Ram%20temple%20under%20the%20aegis%20of%20the%20Modi%20government%C2%A0represents%20the%20triumph%20of%20religious%20fundamentalism%20over%20secularism.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fdelirium-over-ram-mandir-a-nation-consecrated-or-desecrated%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22State%20of%20emergency%20declared%20after%20rioting%20and%20looting%20kills%2016%20in%20Papua%20New%20Guinea%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704957300000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F24%2F01%2F70x70%2Fskynews-papua-new-guinea-riots_6418006.jpg%3F20240111092049%22%2C%22origin