enocide-what-can-the-un-do-about-it%2Famp_articleshow%2F106719453.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Fsouth-africa-says-israels-campaign-in-gaza-amounts-to-genocide-what-can-the-un-do-about-it%2Famp_articleshow%2F106719453.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Taiwan%20presidential%20hopeful%20Hou%20promises%20to%20boost%20island's%20defence%20and%20restart%20talks%20with%20China%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704952383000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-106719502%2Cimgsize-1201795.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Ftaiwan-presidential-hopeful-hou-promises-to-boost-islands-defence-and-restart-talks-with-china%2Farticleshow%2F106719215.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F106719215.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3E%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Ftaiwan-presidential-hopeful-hou-promises-to-boost-islands-defence-and-restart-talks-with-china%2Farticleshow%2F106719215.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm-timesofindia-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Ftaiwan-presidential-hopeful-hou-promises-to-boost-islands-defence-and-restart-talks-with-china%2Famp_articleshow%2F106719215.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Ftaiwan-presidential-hopeful-hou-promises-to-boost-islands-defence-and-restart-talks-with-china%2Famp_articleshow%2F106719215.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Why%20an%20Exploitative%20Labour%20Regime%20Doesn't%20Deter%20Rising%20Undocumented%20Migrants%20in%20the%20US%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F11111216%2FEffect-60.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20United%20States%20has%20long%20been%20a%20beacon%20of%20hope%20for%20global%20migrants%2C%20attracting%20people%20from%20around%20the%20world%20with%20the%20promise%20of%20economic%20opportunity.%20However%2C%20beneath%20the%20surface%20of%20this%20migration%20phenomenon%20lies%20a%20complex%20interplay%20of%20economics%20and%20policy%2C%20particularly%20concerning%20undocumented%20migrants.%20These%20individuals%2C%20often%20unseen%20and%20under-discussed%20in%20the%20mainstream%20narrative%2C%20play%20a%20significant%20role%20in%20the%20American%20economy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20economy%20is%20characterised%20by%20high%20employment%20and%20significant%20gender%20parity%20in%20the%20workforce.%20Most%20American%20households%20have%20multiple%20earners%2C%20contributing%20to%20higher%20overall%20household%20income.%20Despite%20a%20long-term%20unemployment%20rate%20slightly%20above%205.5%25%2C%20the%20US%20maintained%20a%20low%20unemployment%20rate%20of%203.7%25%20in%202023.%20Concurrently%2C%20the%20long-term%20economic%20growth%20rate%20has%20been%20stable%2C%20approximately%20at%203.12%25.%20This%20robust%20economic%20performance%2C%20however%2C%20comes%20with%20its%20challenges%2C%20such%20as%20labour%20shortages%20in%20various%20sectors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMigration%20policies%20and%20the%20workforce%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20has%20a%20complex%20yet%20effective%20set%20of%20migration%20policies%20and%20is%20a%20major%20destination%20for%20international%20students%2C%20many%20of%20whom%20join%20the%20American%20workforce%2C%20fulfilling%20the%20demand%20for%20educated%20and%20skilled%20labour.%20Additionally%2C%20the%20US%20economy%20relies%20significantly%20on%20outsourcing%20technologically%20enabled%20tasks%2C%20particularly%20to%20China%2C%20India%2C%20and%20other%20developing%20economies.%20According%20to%20PEW%20Research%2C%20in%202017%20out%20of%2045%20million%20(13.7%25%20of%20population)%20immigrants%20in%20the%20US%2C%2010.5%20million%20were%20undocumented%2C%20making%20up%20about%203.2%25%20of%20the%20US%20population.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20necessary%20to%20understand%20the%20glut%20in%20absolute%20numbers%20of%20illegal%20and%20undocumented%20immigrants%20in%20the%20US%20in%20association%20with%20the%20puzzle%20of%20US%20minimum%20wage%20rates.%20The%20minimum%20wage%20policy%20in%20the%20US%20is%20a%20contentious%20issue%2C%20with%20significant%20variations%20across%20states.%20The%20federal%20minimum%20wage%20stood%20at%20a%20modest%20%247.25%20per%20hour%20in%202023.%20However%2C%2030%20states%20have%20set%20higher%20minimum%20wages%2C%20with%20the%20highest%20being%20%2442%2C%20and%20the%20lowest%20at%20%2417%20per%20hour.%20The%20national%20average%20hovers%20just%20under%20%2426%20per%20hour.%20This%20disparity%20in%20wages%20is%20a%20key%20factor%20driving%20undocumented%20immigration%2C%20particularly%20across%20the%20southern%20US-Mexico%20border.%20It%20should%20also%20be%20noted%20that%20many%20illegal%20migrants%20and%20F1%20visa%20holders%20who%20work%20on%20the%20sly%20will%20get%20as%20low%20as%20%245%20per%20hour%20of%20work%2C%20making%20it%20the%20most%20exploitative%20labour%20force%20regime%20in%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Findians-detained-illegally-enter-us-border-data%5C%22%3ESince%202019%2C%201.49%20Lakh%20Indians%20Detained%20While%20Trying%20to%20Illegally%20Enter%20US%20Border%3A%20Data%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUndocumented%20immigration%20is%20an%20economic%20necessity%20in%20the%20US%20and%20the%20two%20major%20contesting%20political%20parties%20use%20this%20not%20only%20to%20politicise%20voting%20behaviour%20but%20also%20entice%20private%20investors%20and%20businesses%20which%20can%20do%20with%20an%20illiterate%20labour%20force.%20Thus%2C%20the%20influx%20of%20undocumented%20migrants%20is%20often%20a%20result%20of%20economic%20necessity%2C%20driven%20by%20the%20disparity%20in%20wage%20rates%20and%20the%20demand%20for%20labour%20in%20certain%20sectors.%20These%20immigrants%20find%20employment%20in%20infrastructure%2C%20hospitality%2C%20small%20businesses%2C%20and%20agriculture.%20Notably%2C%20they%20often%20receive%20formal%20documentation%20within%20months%20of%20arrival%20and%20can%20become%20naturalised%20within%20a%20couple%20of%20years%20%E2%80%93%20a%20process%20significantly%20faster%20than%20for%20those%20on%20H1B%20and%20F1%20visas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20impact%20on%20household%20economics%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20US%20national%20residential%20rental%20average%20consuming%2030%25%20of%20median%20household%20income%20(and%20over%2050%25%20for%20the%20lowest%20income%20quintile)%2C%20individuals%20earning%20federal%20minimum%20wage%20or%20working%20unofficially%20face%20significant%20financial%20strain.%20Many%20immigrants%2C%20including%20the%20undocumented%2C%20take%20substantial%20risks%20to%20enter%20the%20US%2C%20motivated%20by%20the%20possibility%20of%20sending%20remittances%20back%20to%20their%20home%20countries.%20For%20example%2C%20the%20average%20daily%20wage%20in%20India%20is%20low%2C%20making%20even%20modest%20savings%20in%20the%20US%20significant%20enough%20to%20justify%20the%20risks%20of%20migration.%20Even%20the%20take-home%2C%20for%20example%2C%20of%20an%20Uber%20operator%20which%20can%20be%20as%20high%20as%20%244%2C000%20per%20month%20in%20the%20US%20is%20hovering%20around%20%24300%20(Rs%2025%2C000)%20per%20month%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Ffour-us-donkey-flights-had-left-for-nicaragua-when-french-immigration-intercepted-legend-airlines%23%3A~%3Atext%3DThe%2520Wire%2520accessed%2520the%2520list%2Cto%2520Mumbai%2520on%2520December%252027.%5C%22%3EFour%20%E2%80%98US%20Donkey%20Flights%E2%80%99%20Had%20Left%20for%20Nicaragua%20When%20French%20Immigration%20Intercepted%20Legend%20Airlines%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUndocumented%20workers%20in%20the%20US%20typically%20earn%20a%20low%20of%20%241000%20per%20month%20(some%20also%20receive%20accommodation%20as%20part%20of%20their%20employment).%20The%20money%20sent%20back%20home%20%E2%80%93%20even%20if%20it%E2%80%99s%20as%20little%20as%20%24300%20per%20month%20%E2%80%93%20translates%20into%20a%20substantial%20amount%20in%20Indian%20currency%2C%20providing%20considerable%20support%20to%20families%20in%20India.%20This%20economic%20incentive%20is%20a%20major%20factor%20driving%20migration%2C%20often%20through%20risky%20and%20illegal%20channels.%20Obvious%20that%20they%20reside%20in%20extremely%20rundown%20residential%20areas%20and%20even%20share%20a%20bed%20on%20a%20rotational%20basis.%20In%20this%20context%2C%20it%20is%20important%20to%20note%20that%20the%20immigrants%20(also%20undocumented)%20take%20risks%20to%20enter%20the%20US%20in%20the%20hope%20of%20savings%20and%20remittances%20to%20their%20dependents%20back%20in%20their%20country%20of%20origin.%20Thus%2C%20in%20the%20US%2C%20a%20saving%20of%20%2410%20to%20%2420%20a%20day%20is%20enough%20to%20take%20extremely%20high-risk%20migrating%20routes%20even%20by%20paying%20high%20costs%20as%20evidenced%20by%20the%20recent%20example%20of%20a%20chartered%20plane%20from%20India%20to%20Nicaragua%2C%20which%20was%20stranded%20in%20France.%20It%20could%20also%20mean%20taking%20a%20life-threatening%20one-way%20trip%20in%20a%20shop%20container.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20we%20speak%20over%20100%2C000%20Indians%20have%20entered%20the%20US%20through%20the%20%E2%80%98Dunki%E2%80%99%20routes%20which%20are%20well%20depicted%20in%20last%20week%E2%80%99s%20movie%20release%20of%20the%20same%20name%20produced%20by%20Rajkumar%20Hirani%20and%20acted%20by%20highly%20acclaimed%20acters%20%E2%80%93%20Shah%20Rukh%20Khan%2C%20Taapsee%20Pannu%2C%20and%20Vicky%20Kaushal.%20Illegal%20migration%20from%20India%2C%20however%2C%20is%20not%20happening%20from%20households%20that%20are%20poor%2C%20but%20rather%20from%20those%20which%20can%20afford%20to%20pay%20high%20fees%20for%20human%20traffickers%2C%20smugglers%2C%20and%20those%20dealing%20with%20hawala%20transactions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAbusaleh%20Shariff%20is%20with%20the%20US-India%20Policy%20Institute%2C%20Washington%20DC%2C%20and%20Centre%20for%20Research%20and%20Debates%20in%20Development%20Policy%2C%20New%20Delhi%20and%20Bengaluru.%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704952062000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F11111216%2FEffect-60.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flabour%2Fwhy-an-exploitative-labour-regime-doesnt-deter-rising-undocumented-migrants-in-the-us%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22About%2010.5%20million%20illegal%20migrants%2C%20who%20made%20perilous%20journeys%20to%20reach%20the%20US%2C%20help%20run%20the%20American%20economy%20even%20working%20at%20an%20hourly%20rate%20as%20low%20as%20%245.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flabour%2Fwhy-an-exploitative-labour-regime-doesnt-deter-rising-undocumented-migrants-in-the-us%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Is%20%E2%80%98Let%E2%80%99s%20Seek%20Peace%20on%20the%20Border%E2%80%99%20Narrative%20About%20Modi%20Government%E2%80%99s%20Intent%20to%20Appease%20China%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F04%2F07085318%2FChina-india.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20ongoing%20border%20crisis%20with%20China%2C%20which%20came%20to%20light%20in%20May%202020%2C%20has%20been%20shrouded%20in%20mystery%20by%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%E2%80%99s%20refusal%20to%20acknowledge%20the%20severity%20and%20intent%20of%20the%20Chinese%20challenge%20in%20Ladakh.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20ingress%20by%20soldiers%20of%20the%20People%E2%80%99s%20Liberation%20Army%20(PLA)%20has%20created%20a%20situation%2C%20as%20confirmed%20by%20a%20senior%20police%20official%E2%80%99s%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcaravanmagazine.in%2Fsecurity%2Ffull-text-sp-ladakh-india-lost-access-patrolling-points-china-border%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ereport%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20where%20Indian%20soldiers%20are%20unable%20to%20reach%2026%20of%20the%2065%20patrolling%20points%20in%20Ladakh%20which%20it%20was%20accessing%20before%202020.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%2020%20rounds%20of%20talks%20between%20corps%20commanders%2C%20the%20Chinese%20side%20has%20not%20agreed%20to%20Indian%20proposals%20for%20disengagement%20in%20Depsang%20and%20Demchok%2C%20or%20for%20de-escalation%20in%20the%20five%20areas%20where%20disengagement%20has%20taken%20place.%20There%20has%20been%20no%20tangible%20progress%20in%20border%20talks%20after%20September%202022%2C%20while%20Beijing%20has%20flatly%20rejected%20any%20calls%20for%20a%20return%20to%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Estatus%20quo%20ante%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENow%20even%20Indian%20military%20officials%2C%20following%20the%20line%20set%20by%20external%20affairs%20minister%20S.%20Jaishankar%2C%20have%20stopped%20mentioning%20the%20phrase%20%E2%80%98%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Estatus%20quo%20ante%E2%80%99%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20and%20no%20longer%20appear%20to%20be%20pressing%20the%20demand%20for%20full%20restoration%20of%20patrolling%20rights%20on%20the%20border.%20This%20has%20raised%20suspicions%20about%20the%20concessionary%20intentions%20of%20the%20Modi%20government%20%E2%80%93%20perhaps%20in%20the%20run-up%20to%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20%E2%80%93%20in%20somehow%20declaring%20the%20border%20crisis%20with%20China%20as%20%E2%80%9Cresolved%E2%80%9D%20even%20at%20the%20cost%20of%20unfavourable%20terms%20for%20India.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20biggest%20indication%20of%20this%20new%20approach%20came%20from%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fsituation-on-china-border-in-ladakh-stable-but-sensitive-not-normal-northern-army-commander%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ean%20interview%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20given%20by%20the%20Northern%20Army%20Commander%2C%20Lt%20Gen%20Upendra%20Dwivedi%2C%20who%20claimed%20that%20there%20has%20been%20a%20%E2%80%9Cpersistent%20approach%20from%20both%20sides%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Cwe%20are%20looking%20at%20%5Bways%20so%5D%20that%20mutual%20concerns%20are%20addressed%E2%80%9D.%20He%20desisted%20from%20criticising%20the%20Chinese%20in%20any%20way%2C%20instead%20arguing%20that%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20aim%20is%20that%20basically%20we%20are%20looking%20at%20peace%20and%20stability.%20We%20want%20to%20prevent%20violence%2C%20so%20keeping%20these%20two%20factors%20and%20give%20negotiations%20the%20time%20%E2%80%93%20to%20gain%20time%20this%20%5Bcreation%20of%20buffer%20zones%5D%20is%20the%20only%20way%20forward.%E2%80%9D%20The%20emphasis%20on%20negotiations%20and%20%E2%80%98positive%20approach%E2%80%99%20from%20China%2C%20when%20the%20PLA%20has%20made%20territorial%20advances%20on%20the%20ground%20and%20denied%20Indian%20soldiers%20its%20hitherto%20exercised%20patrolling%20rights%20is%20baffling.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F09%2F16225700%2FDepsang-map.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F09%2F16225700%2FDepsang-map.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F09%2F16225700%2FDepsang-map-300x225.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F09%2F16225700%2FDepsang-map-1024x768.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-479789%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EThe%20PLA%20has%20denied%20the%20Indian%20Army%E2%80%99s%20patrols%20access%20to%20five%20patrol%20points%20%E2%80%93%20PP%2010%2C%2011%2C%2011a%2C%2012%20and%2013%20%E2%80%93%20by%20blocking%20them%20at%20Bottleneck%2FY%20junction%20around%2018%20km%20inside%20the%20LAC.%20Map%3A%20The%20Wire.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGen%20Dwivedi%E2%80%99s%20interview%20came%20days%20after%20some%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbooks%2Fagnipath-to-galwan-clash-ex-army-chief-general-naravanes-big-revelations-in-memoirs-yet-to-be-released%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eextracts%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20from%20the%20forthcoming%20memoirs%20of%20former%20army%20chief%2C%20Gen%20M.M.%20Naravane%20were%20published%20by%20PTI.%20Naravane%20handled%20the%20China%20border%20crisis%2C%20including%20the%20Galwan%20clash%2C%20at%20its%20peak%20and%20his%20revelations%20were%20not%20kind%20towards%20China%20or%20President%20Xi%20Jingping.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETalking%20about%20the%20Galwan%20clash%20in%20June%202020%2C%20where%2020%20Indian%20soldiers%20and%20at%20least%20four%20Chinese%20soldiers%20died%2C%20Naravane%20wrote%2C%20%E2%80%9CJune%2016%20is%20(Chinese%20President)%20Xi%20Jinping%E2%80%99s%20birthday.%20This%20is%20not%20a%20day%20he%20will%20forget%20any%20time%20soon.%20For%20the%20first%20time%20in%20over%20two%20decades%2C%20the%20Chinese%20and%20the%20PLA%20had%20suffered%20fatal%20casualties.%E2%80%9D%20He%20also%20wrote%20about%20the%20political%20directions%20given%20to%20him%20on%2031%20August%202020%2C%20after%20the%20threat%20of%20a%20full-blown%20conflict%20with%20the%20PLA%20in%20the%20Kailash%20Range%20became%20real.%20Rajnath%20Singh%2C%20the%20defence%20minister%2C%20called%20him%20at%20night%20and%20%E2%80%9Csaid%20that%20he%20had%20spoken%20to%20the%20PM%20and%20that%20it%20was%20purely%20a%20military%20decision.%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3EJo%20ucchit%20samjho%20woh%20karo%20%3C%2Fem%3E(Do%20whatever%20you%20deem%20is%20appropriate).%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CI%20had%20been%20handed%20a%20hot%20potato.%20With%20this%20carte%20blanche%2C%20the%20onus%20was%20now%20totally%20on%20me.%20I%20took%20a%20deep%20breath%20and%20sat%20silently%20for%20a%20few%20minutes.%20All%20was%20quiet%20save%20for%20the%20ticking%20of%20the%20wall%20clock%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%20He%20passed%20orders%20to%20the%20Northern%20Army%20Commander%20%E2%80%9Cto%20move%20a%20troop%20of%20our%20tanks%20right%20to%20the%20forward%20slopes%20of%20the%20Pass%20and%20depress%20their%20guns%20so%20that%20the%20PLA%20would%20be%20staring%20down%20the%20barrels%20of%20our%20guns%E2%80%9D.%20The%20Northern%20Army%20Commander%20had%20%E2%80%9Crecommended%20that%20the%20only%20way%20to%20stop%20the%20PLA%20was%20by%20opening%20up%20with%20our%20own%20medium%20artillery%2C%20which%20he%20said%20was%20ready%20and%20waiting%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fagnipath-scheme-bolt-out-of-the-blue-navy-air-force-former-army-chief-naravane-memoirs%5C%22%3EAgnipath%20Scheme%20Was%20%E2%80%98Bolt%20Out%20of%20the%20Blue%E2%80%99%20for%20Navy%20and%20Air%20Force%3A%20Former%20Army%20Chief%20Naravane%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHis%20memoirs%20are%20now%20ensnared%20in%20some%20sort%20of%20national%20security%20vetting%20process%20by%20the%20government%20and%20are%20unlikely%20to%20see%20the%20light%20of%20day.%20India%E2%80%99s%20corporate-owned%20big%20media%2C%20including%20correspondents%20covering%20national%20security%2C%20have%20let%20Naravane%E2%80%99s%20explosive%20disclosures%20sink%20without%20a%20trace.%20The%20primary%20aim%20is%20to%20prevent%20an%20embarrassment%20to%20the%20Modi%20government%20over%20its%20handling%20of%20the%20crisis%2C%20but%20the%20secondary%20goal%20seems%20to%20be%20to%20avoid%20creating%20a%20strong%20anti-China%20narrative%20in%20the%20public%20space.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENaravane%20himself%20now%20seems%20to%20have%20sensed%20the%20official%20mood.%20In%20his%20latest%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheprint.in%2Fopinion%2Findia-must-use-dialogue-to-solve-border-conflict-with-china-military-solution-not-viable%2F1914201%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ecolumn%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20he%20argued%20that%20because%20%E2%80%9CIndia%20and%20China%20are%20now%20facing%20off%20in%20Eastern%20Ladakh%20for%20the%20fourth%20successive%20winter%2C%E2%80%9D%20India%20must%20consider%20that%20the%20%E2%80%9Ctime%20is%20ripe%2C%20therefore%2C%20for%20negotiations%20to%20recommence%2C%20not%20just%20for%20the%20remaining%20friction%20points%20but%20for%20resolving%20the%20overall%20boundary%20question%E2%80%9D.%20Clearly%2C%20the%20optics%20are%20being%20built%20for%20creating%20an%20environment%20in%20which%20India%20accepts%20a%20negotiated%20solution%20that%20reinforces%20China%E2%80%99s%20aggression%20on%20the%20Ladakh%20border.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFormer%20foreign%20Secretary%20Vijay%20Gokhale%20last%20month%20published%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcarnegieindia.org%2F2023%2F12%2F15%2Fstabilizing-border-possible-way-ahead-in-post-galwan-situation-pub-91244%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Epaper%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20at%20Carnegie%20India%20where%20he%20laid%20out%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20options%20that%20might%20be%20available%20to%20India%20to%20build%20back%20a%20framework%20for%20peace%20and%20tranquility%20along%20the%20border%20areas%E2%80%9D.%20He%20further%20outlined%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20actions%20that%20India%20might%20consider%20adopting%20unilaterally%20as%20well%20as%20in%20the%20negotiations%20with%20China%20with%20the%20objective%20of%20creating%20the%20conditions%20for%20restoration%20of%20peace%20and%20tranquility%20in%20the%20border%20region%E2%80%9D.%20His%20suggestions%20are%20exhaustive%20and%20unobjectionable%20but%20the%20underlying%20premise%20is%20that%20India%20must%20accept%20the%20new%20reality%20on%20the%20China%20border%20and%20somehow%20find%20a%20way%20to%20restore%20%E2%80%9Cpeace%20and%20tranquility%E2%80%9D%20in%20the%20border%20areas.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20a%20similar%20vein%2C%20former%20Northern%20Army%20Commander%20Lt.%20Gen%20D.S.%20Hooda%20(retd.)%20has%20suggested%20in%20a%20recent%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.delhipolicygroup.org%2Fpublication%2Fpolicy-briefs%2Fstabilising-the-line-of-actual-control-need-for-new-protocols.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Epolicy%20brief%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20the%20adoption%20of%20%E2%80%9Ca%20limited%20and%20measured%20approach%20to%20breaking%20the%20impasse%20at%20the%20LAC%2C%20where%20India%20and%20China%20can%20look%20at%20calming%20the%20military%20situation%20with%20quiet%20political%20endorsement%E2%80%9D.%20Asking%20for%20jointly%20identifying%20disputed%20areas%20on%20the%20LAC%2C%20he%20suggests%20that%20%E2%80%9Ceither%20no-patrolling%20buffer%20zones%20could%20be%20established%20or%20patrolling%20patterns%20agreed%20upon%20with%20a%20specified%20periodicity%20to%20avoid%20face-offs%20between%20opposing%20troops.%20Additional%20hotlines%20and%20meeting%20points%20should%20come%20up%20along%20the%20LAC%20to%20resolve%20any%20local%20incident%20promptly%E2%80%9D.%20The%20whole%20idea%20seems%20to%20be%20rooted%20in%20a%20need%20to%20quickly%20end%20the%20crisis%2C%20even%20if%20the%20Chinese%20continue%20to%20hold%20an%20upper%20hand.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIs%20the%20sudden%20plethora%20of%20articles%20providing%20justifications%20for%20an%20Indian%20engagement%20with%20China%20to%20%E2%80%9Cresolve%E2%80%9D%20the%20border%20crisis%20a%20coincidence%3F%20Or%20is%20it%20driven%20by%20the%20political%20need%20to%20create%20a%20narrative%20where%20a%20negotiated%20settlement%20that%20rewards%20Chinese%20aggression%20on%20the%20border%20is%20seen%20as%20the%20only%20viable%20option%3F%20As%20Major%20General%20Ashok%20Mehta%20(retd.)%20recently%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tribuneindia.com%2Fnews%2Fcomment%2Fhow-ambitious-india-fares-in-catching-up-with-china-579472%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ewrote%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20the%20establishment%20is%20gripped%20by%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20fear%20of%20annoying%20China%20and%20escalating%20the%20conflict%E2%80%9D.%20He%20claimed%20that%20there%20are%20%E2%80%9Cno%20buyers%20for%20conducting%20any%20game-changing%20operation%20similar%20to%20Snow%20Leopard%20on%20land%20or%20at%20sea%20or%20exploiting%20China%E2%80%99s%20Malacca%20dilemma%E2%80%9D.%20The%20Modi%20government%20needs%20to%20shed%20%E2%80%9Cdiffidence%20and%20deference%E2%80%9D%20towards%20China.%20A%20determined%20approach%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20need%20the%20narrative%20that%20is%20being%20constructed%20now.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704951238000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F04%2F07085318%2FChina-india.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fis-lets-seek-peace-on-the-border-narrative-about-modi-governments-intent-to-appease-china%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20optics%20are%20being%20built%20for%20creating%20an%20environment%20in%20which%20India%20accepts%20an%20unfavourable%20negotiated%20solution%20that%20reinforces%20and%20rewards%20China%E2%80%99s%20aggression%20on%20the%20Ladakh%20border.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fis-lets-seek-peace-on-the-border-narrative-about-modi-g