%20and%20featured%20fake%20hosts%20and%20voice%20overs.%20The%20Chinese%20Ministry%20of%20State%20Security%20is%20believed%20to%20be%20behind%20this%20informational%20operation%2C%20as%20the%20videos%20contained%20Chinese%20phrases%20not%20commonly%20used%20in%20Taiwan.%20Taiwan%E2%80%99s%20voters%20will%20choose%20a%20new%20leader%20on%20Saturday%20as%20Tsai%20is%20set%20to%20step%20down%20after%20serving%20the%20maximum%20two%20terms.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fchina-may-be-behind-fake-videos-of-taiwan-president%2Farticleshow%2F106715776.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm-timesofindia-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fchina-may-be-behind-fake-videos-of-taiwan-president%2Famp_articleshow%2F106715776.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fchina-may-be-behind-fake-videos-of-taiwan-president%2Famp_articleshow%2F106715776.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Why%204%20Highest%20Gurus%20of%20Sanatan%20Hindu%20Dharma%20Won't%20Participate%20in%20Ram%20Temple%20Pranpratistha%2C'%20Explains%20Pro-Hindutva%20Portal%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F11092938%2FGDY7syJb0AAYFyc.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20top%20spiritual%20leaders%20in%20Sanatan%20Hindu%20Dharma%2C%20Jagatguru%20Shankaracharyas%2C%20won%E2%80%99t%20be%20part%20of%20the%20ceremony%20to%20inaugurate%20the%20Shri%20Ram%20Temple%20in%20Ayodhya%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Struggle%20for%20Hindu%20Existence%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22about%3Ablank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ereported%20on%20January%207.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20It%20is%20an%20avowedly%20pro-Hindutva%20portal%20dedicated%2C%20it%20says%2C%20to%20protect%20and%20struggle%20for%20Hindus%20globally.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20involvement%20of%20PM%20Narendra%20Modi%20as%20the%20%E2%80%9Cchief%20host%E2%80%9D%20in%20the%20programme%20%E2%80%9Chas%20stirred%20concerns%E2%80%9D%20among%20senior%20seers%20over%20the%20proposed%20consecration%20ceremony%20scheduled%20for%20January%2022%20in%20Ayodhya.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20feel%20that%20this%20places%20him%20at%20the%20forefront%20of%20the%20event%2C%20potentially%20undermining%20the%20traditional%20rituals%20dictated%20by%20the%20Sanatan%20Shastras.%20Despite%20the%20general%20excitement%20for%20the%20Ram%20Temple%20Consecration%2C%20the%20absence%20of%20Shankaracharyas%20is%20a%20point%20of%20contention%20among%20devout%20Hindus%2C%E2%80%9D%20reports%20the%20portal.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98A%20tomb%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EShankaracharya%20Swami%20Shri%20Nischalananda%20Saraswati%20of%20Purvaamnaya%20Govardhanmath%20Puri%20peeth%20has%20declined%20participation%20in%20the%20Ayodhya%20Ram%20Mandir%20Pran%20Pratishtha%20programme%2C%20as%20he%20says%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20government%E2%80%99s%20endeavour%20is%20not%20centred%20around%20constructing%20a%20%E2%80%9Csacred%20temple%E2%80%9D%20but%2C%20in%20his%20words%2C%20%E2%80%9Ca%20tomb.%E2%80%9D%20This%20characterisation%20suggests%20a%20perception%20that%20the%20project%20lacks%20the%20sanctity%20and%20reverence%20inherent%20in%20%E2%80%9Ctraditional%20temple%20construction.%E2%80%9D%20His%20decision%20not%20to%20attend%20is%20grounded%20in%20the%20principle%20of%20choosing%20not%20to%20be%20part%20of%20a%20place%20where%20due%20respect%20is%20perceived%20to%20be%20lacking.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20decision%20not%20to%20attend%20the%20event%20is%20rooted%20in%20a%20commitment%20to%20maintaining%20the%20dignity%20and%20glory%20associated%20with%20their%20position.%20The%20reluctance%20to%20participate%20is%20not%20a%20rejection%20of%20reverence%20for%20Shri%20Ram%2C%20but%20rather%20a%20principled%20stand%20against%20what%20is%20perceived%20as%20the%20opportunistic%20and%20manipulative%20politics%20of%20certain%20leaders.%20This%20stance%20emphasises%20the%20independence%20and%20moral%20integrity%20of%20the%20spiritual%20leadership%2C%20free%20from%20what%20is%20considered%20as%20the%20influence%20of%20%E2%80%9Ccrooked%E2%80%9D%20political%20figures.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98Still%20under%20construction%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EShankaracharya%20Swami%20Shri%20Bharati%20Teerth%20Ji%20of%20Sringeri%20Sharda%20Peeth%20has%20reportedly%20declined%20the%20invitation%20to%20despite%20expressing%20joy%20about%20the%20construction%20of%20the%20Ram%20temple.%20His%20reservations%20stem%20from%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20temple%20is%20still%20under%20construction.%20He%20deems%20it%20inappropriate%20to%20consecrate%20the%20divine%20in%20a%20structure%20that%20is%20not%20yet%20complete%2C%20citing%20concerns%20about%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20righteousness%20of%20such%20an%20act.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20has%20flagged%20his%20concern%20on%20the%20simultaneous%20construction%20of%20what%20is%20purported%20to%20be%20Asia%E2%80%99s%20largest%20mosque%20in%20Ayodhya.%20This%2C%20for%20him%2C%20%E2%80%9Cmarks%20an%20unfortunate%20turn%20of%20events.%E2%80%9D%20The%20dissatisfaction%20is%20further%20accentuated%20by%20a%20sense%20of%20neglect%2C%20as%20he%20claims%20that%20he%2C%20along%20with%20other%20revered%20figures%2C%20had%20presented%20evidence%20in%20court%20regarding%20the%20Ram%20Mandir.%20However%2C%20according%20to%20his%20statement%2C%20the%20Ram%20Mandir%20Trust%20has%20not%20sought%20advice%20from%20them%20or%20their%20representatives%2C%20suggesting%20a%20lack%20of%20consultation%20with%20key%20spiritual%20leaders.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20per%20the%20portal%2C%20the%20Shankaracharya%20has%20accused%20the%20Modi%20government%20of%20having%20a%20duplicitous%20character.%20He%20contends%20that%20the%20government%2C%20despite%20executing%20the%20construction%20of%20the%20Ram%20temple%2C%20is%20perceived%20%E2%80%9Cas%20exploiting%20Hindu%20sentiments%20for%20political%20gains.%E2%80%9D%20This%20assertion%20reflects%20a%20broader%20scepticism%20about%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20intentions%20and%20commitment%20to%20the%20holistic%20well-being%20of%20the%20religious%20community.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20suitable%20time%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EShankaracharya%20Shri%20Swami%20Sadanand%20Saraswati%20of%20Paschimannaya%20Dwarka%20Shardapeeth%20has%20chosen%20not%20to%20participate%20in%20the%20Ram%20Mandir%20Mahotsav%2C%20citing%20concerns%20around%20the%20timing%20of%20the%20consecration%2C%20stating%20that%20in%20the%20inauspicious%20month%20of%20Paush%2C%20according%20to%20scriptures%2C%20the%20initiation%20of%20life%20consecration%20in%20deities%20is%20deemed%20inappropriate.%20He%20proposes%20that%20a%20more%20suitable%20time%20would%20be%20Ram%20Navami%2C%20the%20auspicious%20birth%20day%20of%20Lord%20Rama.%20A%20central%20point%20of%20contention%20is%20the%20perceived%20%E2%80%9Cpoliticisation%20of%20the%20event.%E2%80%9D%20Swami%20Sadanand%20Saraswati%20suggests%20that%20politics%20is%20the%20primary%20reason%20for%20the%20consecration%20happening%20at%20this%20moment.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20anticipates%20that%20the%20election%20code%20of%20conduct%20will%20be%20in%20force%20during%20Ram%20Navami%2C%20making%20it%20less%20advantageous%20for%20BJP%20leaders%20to%20exploit%20the%20consecration%20for%20political%20gain.%20This%20perspective%20introduces%20a%20political%20dimension%20to%20the%20decision-making%20process%20around%20the%20temple%20consecration.%20Additionally%2C%20Swami%20Sadanand%20Saraswati%20questions%20the%20rationale%20behind%20consecrating%20the%20temple%20before%20its%20completion.%20Drawing%20an%20analogy%2C%20he%20notes%20that%20traditionally%2C%20one%20does%20not%20enter%20a%20house%20until%20it%20is%20fully%20formed.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98Anti-%3Cem%3Edharamashashtra%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%98%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EShankaracharya%20Swami%20Shri%20Avimukteshwarananda%20Saraswati%20of%20Uttaramnaya%20Jyotirmath%20has%20decided%20not%20to%20attend%20the%20Ayodhya%20event%20on%20January%2022%2C%20citing%20specific%20concerns%2C%20which%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fits-a-ram-mandir-ramanand-tradition-to-be-followed-temple-trusts-secy-remarks-draw-criticism%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ereported%20on%20January%209%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20The%20report%20cited%20him%20as%20saying%2C%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3EHum%3C%2Fem%3E%20anti-Modi%20%3Cem%3Enahi%20hain%2C%20lekin%20hum%20anti-dharamashashtra%20bhi%20nahi%20hona%20chahte%3C%2Fem%3E%20(We%20are%20not%20anti-Modi%2C%20but%20we%20do%20not%20want%20to%20be%20anti-dharamashashtra%20either)%2C%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%20This%20portal%20says%20that%20his%20assertion%20is%20that%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20Vedas%2C%20foundational%20texts%20in%20Hinduism%2C%20contain%20a%20distinctive%20provision%20for%20the%20role%20of%20priesthood%2C%20reserving%20it%20for%20Brahmins.%20According%20to%20Vedic%20traditions%2C%20the%20priesthood%20is%20considered%20exclusive%20to%20the%20Brahmin%20caste.%20Swami%20Avimukteshwarananda%20Saraswati%20emphasises%20the%20significance%20of%20adhering%20to%20these%20established%20practices%20outlined%20in%20the%20Vedas.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20has%20criticised%20the%20appointment%20of%20a%20Shudra%20as%20a%20temple%20priest%2C%20viewing%20it%20as%20a%20departure%20from%20the%20religious%20principles%20outlined%20in%20the%20Vedas.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20portal%20writes%20that%20it%20%E2%80%9Cis%20also%20unfortunate%20that%20once%20Narendra%20Modi%20was%20seen%20at%20the%20feet%20of%20Shankaracharyas%20to%20get%20blessings%20for%20his%20political%20prosperity%2C%20who%20is%20%E2%80%98now%20playing%20an%20adharmik%20role%20to%20undermine%20the%20Sanatan%20values%20and%20dignities%E2%80%99%E2%80%9D.%20It%20says%20that%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20non-participation%20of%20Highest%20Dharma%20gurus%20of%20Hindu%20Dharma%20in%20the%20most%20awaited%20Ram%20temple%20consecration%20is%20really%20unfortunate.%20It%20is%20not%20only%20a%20religious%20setback%20but%20also%20carries%20broader%20social%20and%20political%20implications.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESringeri%20Sankaracharya%20Sri%20Bharati%20Teerth%20Mahaswamy%20Ji%20has%20conveyed%20his%20blessings%20that%20every%20Astika%20must%20take%20part%20in%20the%20most%20sacred%20and%20rare%20Prana-pratistha%20in%20Ayodhya%20on%20January%2022%20to%20get%20unbounded%20grace%20of%20Bhagavan%20Sri%20Rama.%20But%2C%20says%20the%20portal%2C%20%E2%80%9Cit%20is%20still%20not%20clear%20from%20the%20message%20whether%20Sringeri%20Shankaracharya%20will%20participate%20in%20the%20Prana-pratistha%20in%20Ayodhya%20or%20not.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704945869000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F11092938%2FGDY7syJb0AAYFyc.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Freligion%2Fsanatan-hindu-dharma-highest-guru-ram-temple%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20prominent%20pro-Hindutva%20portal%2C%20describing%20itself%20as%20adding%20'a%20new%20dimension%20to%20create%20a%20solidarity%20in%20Global%20Hindus'%20quotes%20Shankaracharyas%20critical%20of%20politicisation%2C%20not%20getting%20due%20respect%20and%20ceremony%20being%20done%20before%20time.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A6%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Freligion%2Fsanatan-hindu-dharma-highest-guru-ram-temple%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Where%20Will%20We%20Go%3F'%3A%20Murdered%20UP%20Leader's%20Family%20After%20SC%20Turns%20Down%20Intervention%20in%20Ajay%20Mishra's%20Acquittal%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F08%2F23133018%2FUntitled-design-2022-08-23T133005.324.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20a%20day%20ago%2C%20refused%20to%20intervene%20in%20the%20Allahabad%20high%20court%E2%80%99s%20judgement%20reaffirming%20the%20acquittal%20of%20Union%20minister%20Ajay%20Mishra%20%E2%80%98Teni%E2%80%99%20in%20the%20murder%20case%20of%20Samajwadi%20Party%20youth%20leader%20Prabhat%20Gupta%20in%202000.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETeni%2C%20the%20member%20of%20parliament%20from%20Lakhimpur%20Kheri%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20holds%20the%20Union%20minister%20of%20state%20for%20home%20affairs%20portfolio%20in%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Monday%20(January%208)%2C%20a%20division%20bench%20of%20Justices%20Bela%20M.%20Trivedi%20and%20Pankaj%20Mithal%20dismissed%20a%20special%20leave%20petition%20(SLP)%20filed%20by%20the%20deceased%E2%80%99s%20brother%2C%20Rajeev%20Gupta%2C%20against%20the%20high%20court%20judgment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESenior%20counsel%20Kapil%20Sibal%20appeared%20for%20Gupta.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20bench%20said%20that%20after%20having%20heard%20Sibal%20%E2%80%9Cat%20length%20and%20after%20carefully%20perusing%20the%20material%20placed%20on%20record%2C%20we%20are%20not%20inclined%20to%20interfere%20with%20the%20concurrent%20findings%20of%20facts%20recorded%20by%20the%20two%20Courts.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20the%20UP%20government%20did%20not%20file%20an%20SLP%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20challenging%20the%20high%20court%E2%80%99s%20judgement%20despite%20Gupta%E2%80%99s%20requests%2C%20he%20approached%20the%20top%20court%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20May%2019%2C%202023%2C%20the%20high%20court%20upheld%20the%20acquittal%20of%20Teni%20and%20three%20others%20in%20the%2023-year-old%20murder%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20dismissed%20the%20criminal%20appeal%20and%20revision%20appeal%20filed%20against%20their%20acquittal%20by%20a%20sessions%20court%20in%20Lakhimpur%20Kheri%20in%202004.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20upholding%20the%20trial%20court%20verdict%2C%20the%20high%20court%20said%20the%20%E2%80%9Cprosecution%20has%20utterly%20failed%20to%20establish%20the%20chain%20of%20events%20which%20can%20be%20said%20to%20exclusively%20lead%20to%20the%20one%20and%20only%20conclusion%2C%20i.e.%2C%20the%20guilt%20of%20the%20accused%20persons.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fajay-mishra-2000-murder-case-lakhimpur-kheri%5C%22%3EWho%20Was%20Ajay%20Mishra%20Before%20He%20Became%20a%20Legislator%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20division%20bench%20of%20Justices%20Attau%20Rahman%20Masoodi%20and%20Om%20Prakash%20Shukla%20noted%20that%20the%20%E2%80%9Cevidence%20recorded%20in%20the%20present%20case%20has%20been%20appreciated%20in%20its%20correct%20perspective%20and%20the%20trial%20court%20has%20at%20no%20point%20of%20time%20missed%20the%20woods%20of%20the%20tree.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20court%20has%20also%20recorded%20its%20independent%20finding%20and%20holds%20that%20the%20theory%20put%20forth%20by%20prosecution%20that%20the%20four%20accused%20persons%20were%20liable%20for%20causing%20death%20of%20the%20deceased%20is%20unconvincing%20and%20shorn%20of%20evidence%20proved%20beyond%20reasonable%20doubt%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20the%20high%20court%20bench.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERajeev%20Gupta%2C%20who%20has%20fought%20a%20long%20battle%20to%20get%20justice%20for%20his%20brother%2C%20was%20again%20left%20disappointed%20after%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20dismissed%20his%20SLP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20the%20highest%20authority%20in%20the%20country%2C%20the%20SC%2C%20will%20not%20interfere%2C%20then%20where%20will%20people%20like%20us%20go%20for%20justice%3F%20Where%20will%20the%20victims%20go%3F%E2%80%9D%20Gupta%20asked%20while%20speaking%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESC%20bench%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20December%206%2C%202023%2C%20the%20advocate%20on%20record%20for%20the%20petitioner%2C%20Pragya%20Baghel%2C%20had%20written%20to%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20Registrar%20(Listing)%20requesting%20it%20to%20pass%20%E2%80%9Cappropriate%20orders%E2%80%9D%20so%20that%20the%20matter%20could%20be%20heard%20on%20the%20next%20day%20of%20listing%20before%20the%20bench%20presided%20by%20Justice%20Aniruddha%20Bose.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20the%20rules%20framed%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20the%20matter%20should%20have%20been%20listed%20before%20Justice%20Bose%2C%20said%20Baghel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20matter%20was%2C%20however%2C%20heard%20by%20Justices%20Trivedi%20and%20Mithal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20murder%20case%20dates%20back%20to%202000%2C%20when%20Teni%2C%20today%20a%20prominent%20and%20controversial%20minister%20in%20the%20NDA%20government%2C%20was%20a%20BJP%20worker%20in%20the%20Terai%20district%20of%20Lakhimpur%20Kheri%20and%20was%20yet%20to%20enter%20state-level%20electoral%20politics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20FIR%2C%20Prabhat%20Gupta%20and%20Teni%20had%20a%20rivalry%20over%20panchayat%20elections%20and%20on%20July%208%2C%202000%2C%20when%20Prabhat%20Gupta%20was%20going%20to%20his%20shop%20from%20his%20house%2C%20he%20was%20shot%20at%20on%20his%20temple%20and%20between%20his%20chest%20and%20abdomen.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FfSO4X6rzVXg%3Ffeature%3Doembed%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22840%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Lakhimpur%20Kheri%20Case%3A%20Ajay%20Mishra%20Teni%20Slams%20Reporters%20When%20Asked%20About%20the%20SIT%20Report%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22473%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20fell%20on%20the%20ground%20and%20died%2C%20said%20the%20revision%20petition%20filed%20by%20his%20father%2C%20Santosh%20Gupta%20(now%20deceased)%2C%20in%20the%20high%20court%20in%202004%20following%20the%20trial%20court%20acquittal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETeni%20and%20three%20of%20his%20associates%20were%20accused%20of%20the%20crime.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20accused%20told%20the%20court%20they%20had%20been%20falsely%20implicated%20due%20to%20political%20rivalry%20and%20enmity%20over%20the%20panchayat%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20legal%20battle%20in%20the%20high%20court%20was%20a%20long-drawn%20affair%20marked%20by%20adjournments%20and%20judicial%20delays.%20It%20took%20almost%20two%20decades%20for%20a%20judgement%20to%20finally%20be%20pronounced%20against%20the%20trial%20court%20verdict%20of%202004.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20May%2019%20last%20year%2C%20the%20high%20court%20dismissed%20the%20government%20appeal%20filed%20by%20the%20state%20of%20UP%20and%20the%20revision%20appeal%20filed%20by%20Prabhat%20Gupta%E2%80%99s%20father.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Prabhat%20Gupta%20murder%20case%20had%20been%20long%20forgotten%2C%20until%20Teni%20got%20engulfed%20by%20the%20incident%20of%20the%20mowing%20down%20of%20farmers%20by%20a%20convoy%20of%20cars%20linked%20to%20him%20on%20October%203%2C%202021%20in%20Lakhimpur%20Kheri.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20sprung%20into%20the%20spotlight%20for%20the%20wrong%20reasons%20after%20his%20son%20Ashish%20Mishra%20alias%20Monu%20and%20his%20associates%20were%20accused%20of%20murdering%20four%20farmers%20in%20Tikonia%20by%20mowing%20them%20down%20under%20their%20SUVs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20total%20of%20eight%20persons%20were%20killed%20in%20the%20incident.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThree%20BJP%20workers%2C%20including%20a%20driver%2C%20who%20were%20caught%20by%20the%20enraged%20mob%20of%20protesting%20farmers%20were%20killed%20in%20retaliation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20local%20scribe%2C%20Raman%20Kashyap%2C%20there%20to%20cover%20a%20farmers%E2%80%99%20protest%20against%20controversial%20statements%20made%20by%20Teni%2C%20was%20also%20mowed%20to%20death%20by%20the%20SUVs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fajay-mishra-jailed-farmers-demands-agitation-lakhimpur%5C%22%3E%20%E2%80%98Sack%20Ajay%20Mishra%3B%20Release%20Jailed%20Farmers%E2%80%99%3A%20Demands%20That%20Echoed%20the%2075-Hour%20Agitation%20in%20Lakhimpur%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Teni%E2%80%99s%20son%20Monu%20was%20the%20prime%20accused%20in%20the%20incident%2C%20the%20minister%20also%20found%20himself%20under%20the%20scanner%20after%20it%20surfaced%20that%20it%20was%20his%20provocative%20statements%20that%20had%20allegedly%20triggered%20the%20protests%20by%20farmers%20on%20the%20said%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20September%2025%2C%202021%2C%20while%20warning%20protesting%20farmers%20in%20Lakhimpur%20Kheri%2C%20known%20as%20the%20sugar%20bowl%20of%20UP%2C%20to%20%E2%80%9Cmend%20themselves%E2%80%9D%20or%20else%20he%20would%20not%20take%20more%20than%20two%20minutes%20to%20mend%20them%20himself%2C%20Teni%20had%20also%20reminded%20them%20of%20his%20past%20record%20before%20he%20was%20elected%20a%20public%20representative%20and%20said%20that%20he%20did%20%E2%80%9Cnot%20run%20from%20any%20challenge.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20past%20record%2C%20the%20farmers%20construed%2C%20referred%20to%20the%20murder%20charge%20against%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20responding%20to%20questions%20on%20his%20past%20record%20a%20few%20days%20after%20the%20Tikonia%20incident%20of%202021%2C%20the%20Union%20minister%20stated%20that%20%E2%80%9Call%20cases%20against%20me%20had%20concluded%20in%20my%20favour.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20the%20cases%20lodged%20against%20him%20in%20the%20past%20were%20%E2%80%9Cfake%E2%80%9D%20and%20attempts%20to%20implicate%20him%20had%20%E2%80%9Cfailed%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20he%20was%20elected%20an%20MLA%20in%202012%20and%20MP%20in%202014%20and%202019%2C%20Teni%20served%20as%20the%20vice-president%20of%20the%20district%20cooperative%20bank%20from%202000%20to%202005%20and%20was%20a%20member%20of%20the%20Kheri%20zilla%20panchayat%20from%202005%20to%202010.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704945025000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F08%2F23133018%2FUntitled-design-2022-08-23T133005.324.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Futtar-pradesh-ajay-mishra-teni-supreme-court%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Teni%2C%20the%20member%20of%20parliament%20from%20Lakhimpur%20Kheri%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20holds%20the%20Union%20minister%20of%20state%20for%20home%20affairs%20portfolio%20in%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Futtar-pradesh-ajay-mishra-teni-supreme-court%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22AI-Generated%20George%20Carlin%20Drops%20Comedy%20Special%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704943955000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F05%2Fgeorge-carlin.jpg%3Fw%3D1000%26h%3D562%26crop%3D1%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3D1235868315%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22More%20than%2015%20years%20after%20his%20death%2C%20stand-up%20comedian%20George%20Carlin%20has%20been%20brought%20back%20to%20life%20in%20an%20artificial%20intelligence-generated%20special%20called%20%E2%80%9CGeorge%20Carlin%3A%20I%E2%80%99m%20Glad%20I%E2%80%99m%20Dead.%E2%80%9D%20The%20hour-long%20special%2C%20which%20dropped%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20comes%20from%20Dudesy%2C%20a%20comedy%20AI%20that%20hosts%20a%20podcast%20and%20YouTube%20show%20with%20Mad%20TV%20alum%20Will%2