0that%20the%20ongoing%20conflict%20had%20%E2%80%9Cled%20to%20%5Bthe%5D%20large-scale%20loss%20of%20civilian%20lives%2C%20especially%20women%20and%20children%2C%20and%20has%20resulted%20in%20an%20alarming%20humanitarian%20crisis%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20clearly%20unacceptable%20and%20we%20have%20strongly%20condemned%20the%20death%20of%20civilians%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20she%20added%20that%20India%20was%20%E2%80%9Caware%20that%20the%20immediate%20trigger%20%5Bwas%5D%20the%20terror%20attacks%20in%20Israel%20on%207th%20October%2C%20which%20were%20shocking%20and%20deserve%20our%20unequivocal%20condemnation%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIndia%20has%20a%20zero-tolerance%20approach%20to%20terrorism.%20There%20can%20be%20no%20justifications%20for%20terrorism%20and%20hostage-taking.%20Our%20thoughts%20are%20with%20those%20who%20have%20been%20taken%20as%20hostages%20and%20demand%20their%20immediate%20and%20unconditional%20release%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20statement%20was%20made%20at%20a%20session%20that%20took%20place%20under%20the%20UN%20General%20Assembly%E2%80%99s%20mandate%20to%20meet%20within%2010%20working%20days%20after%20a%20veto%20in%20the%20UN%20Security%20Council.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20December%2022%2C%20the%20US%20had%20vetoed%20an%20amendment%20by%20Russia%20that%20called%20for%20the%20cessation%20of%20hostilities%20in%20Gaza.%20Following%20that%2C%20the%20UN%20Security%20Council%20passed%20a%20resolution%20to%20increase%20humanitarian%20aid%20to%20the%20besieged%20Palestinian%20territory%2C%20with%20a%20vote%20of%2013%20in%20favour%20and%20the%20United%20States%20and%20Russia%20abstaining.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20statement%20praised%20the%20United%20Arab%20Emirates%20for%20piloting%20the%20resolution%20in%20the%20Security%20Council.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStating%20that%20the%20Indian%20leadership%20was%20in%20touch%20with%20its%20counterparts%20in%20Israe